01:49.630 --> 01:52.520
兇猛的食肉動物  溫順的食草動物

01:53.680 --> 01:56.000
但是隨著時間的推移 我們進化了
But over time, we evolved.

01:56.200 --> 01:59.800
並且擺脫了我們原始的野蠻天性
And moved beyond our primitive, savage ways.

02:00.000 --> 02:03.400
現在食肉動物和食草動物和諧共處
Now, predator and prey live in harmony.

02:04.680 --> 02:08.840
每一個年輕的小動物都有了大量的機遇
And every young mammal has multitudinous opportunities.

02:08.920 --> 02:09.920
是的
Yeah.

02:10.280 --> 02:13.520
我不用再躲在羊群中
I don't have to cower in a herd anymore.

02:13.720 --> 02:17.240
並且 我還可以成為一個宇航員
Instead, I can be an astronaut.

02:19.360 --> 02:22.440
我不用再做一個孤單的狩獵者了
I don't have to be a lonely hunter anymore.

02:22.680 --> 02:24.960
現在我可以追捕偷稅漏稅行為
Today, I can hunt for tax exemptions.

02:25.200 --> 02:27.960
我要成為一名精算師
I'm gonna be an actuary!

02:29.360 --> 02:32.280
我可以讓世界變得更美好
And I can make the world a better place.

02:32.520 --> 02:34.090
我將會成為
I am going to be...

02:36.040 --> 02:37.960
一名警察
A police officer!

02:40.560 --> 02:41.800
兔子警察
Bunny cop?

02:41.920 --> 02:44.650
那是我聽過的最蠢的事情
That is the most stupidest thing I ever heard.

02:44.880 --> 02:47.560
這對於思想狹隘的人來說也許是不可能的
It may seem impossible to small minds...

02:47.760 --> 02:49.040
我說你呢 吉迪恩·格雷
I'm looking at you, Gideon Grey.

02:50.720 --> 02:53.400
但是 僅211英里之外
But, just 211 miles away...

02:53.600 --> 02:57.120
坐落著一個偉大的城市 動物城
stands the great city of Zootopia!

02:57.400 --> 03:00.640
我們的祖先在那裏首次簽訂了和平條約
Where our ancestors first joined together in peace...

03:00.880 --> 03:07.200
並且宣告 每個人皆有無限可能
and declared that anyone can be anything!

03:08.840 --> 03:11.080
謝謝大家 晚安
Thank you and good night!

03:11.520 --> 03:13.440
朱迪 你有沒有想過我和你媽媽
Judy, you ever wonder how your mom and me...

03:13.560 --> 03:15.210
為什麼生活得這麼愉快
got to be so darn happy?

03:15.280 --> 03:16.360
沒有
Nope.

03:16.560 --> 03:19.210
因為我們放棄了我們的夢想 然後安定下來 對吧 邦尼
Well, we gave up on our dreams and we settled. Right, Bon?

03:19.400 --> 03:21.560
恩 沒錯 就是這樣 斯圖 我們很安定呢
Oh, yes, that's right, Stu. We settled hard.

03:21.800 --> 03:24.610
你看 這就是知足的好處 朱迪
See, that's the beauty of complacency, Jude.

03:24.800 --> 03:27.040
如果你不嘗試新事物 你就永遠不會失敗
If you don't try anything new, you'll never fail.

03:27.240 --> 03:28.650
實際上 我就喜歡嘗試
I like trying actually.

03:28.880 --> 03:30.240
親愛的 你爸爸的意思是
What you father means, hon...

03:30.480 --> 03:31.920
即使對你來說 要成為一名警察
is it's gonna be difficult...

03:32.080 --> 03:34.400
也會很困難 甚至不可能
impossible even, for you to become a police officer.

03:34.600 --> 03:36.040
好吧 從來沒有過兔子當警察
Right. There's never been a bunny cop.

03:36.120 --> 03:37.280
-沒有過 -兔子們做不來這一行
- No. - Bunnies don't do that.

03:37.320 --> 03:38.320
-從來沒有 -從來沒有
- Never. - Never.

03:38.600 --> 03:41.330
噢 那我就成為第一個吧
Oh. Then, I guess I'll have to be the first one.

03:41.560 --> 03:43.440
因為我要把這個世界
Because I am gonna make...

03:43.600 --> 03:46.120
變得更美好
the world a better place.

03:46.360 --> 03:48.680
或者 你知道的
Or, uh, heck, you know, you want to talk...

03:48.840 --> 03:50.120
想讓世界變得更美好
about making the world a better place...

03:50.360 --> 03:52.080
沒有比種胡蘿蔔更好的實現辦法了
no better way to do it than becoming a carrot farmer.

03:52.280 --> 03:54.120
沒錯 你的爸爸 我
Yes! Your dad, me...

03:54.360 --> 03:56.560
你的二百七十五個兄弟姐妹
your 275 brothers and sisters.

03:56.720 --> 03:58.370
-我們在改變世界 -沒錯
- We're changing the world! - Yeah.

03:58.600 --> 04:00.520
-一個一個蘿蔔來 -完全贊同
- One carrot at a time. - Amen to that.

04:00.680 --> 04:02.160
種胡蘿蔔是一個高尚的職業
Carrot farming is a noble profession.

04:02.200 --> 04:03.200
嗯哼
Mmm-hmm.

04:03.360 --> 04:04.720
把種子放進地裏
Just putting the seeds in the ground.

04:04.920 --> 04:06.600
和土壤融在一起 再用泥土掩蓋
Ah, at one with the soil. Just getting covered in dirt.

04:06.760 --> 04:08.000
你會明白的 親愛的
You get it, honey.

04:08.120 --> 04:09.360
擁有夢想是一件很棒的事情
It's great to have dreams.

04:09.560 --> 04:10.920
當然 只要你不過分相信它
Yeah. Just as long as you don't...

04:10.960 --> 04:12.400
過分相信它
believe in them too much.

04:14.080 --> 04:15.200
她又跑哪去了
Where'd the heck she go?

04:16.280 --> 04:18.120
現在就把你的票給我
Give me your tickets right now...

04:18.200 --> 04:19.530
否則我就要狠狠地踢你的
or I'm gonna kick your...

04:19.640 --> 04:21.080
-小羊屁股 -嗷
- meek little sheep butt. - Ow!

04:21.280 --> 04:22.640
住手 吉迪恩
Cut it out, Gideon!

04:22.800 --> 04:25.200
咩 咩 你想幹什麼 哭嗎
Baa! Baa! What are you gonna do? Cry?

04:25.320 --> 04:28.290
嘿 你聽見她說的話了 住手
Hey! You heard her. Cut it out.

04:28.480 --> 04:30.360
戲服不錯啊 兔崽子
Nice costume, loser.

04:30.600 --> 04:32.520
你以為你生活在什麼瘋狂的世界
What crazy world are you living in...

04:32.640 --> 04:34.920
讓你覺得一個兔子也能當警察
where you think a bunny could be a cop?

04:35.160 --> 04:37.160
乖乖地把我朋友的票還回來
Kindly return my friend's tickets.

04:37.400 --> 04:38.480
來拿啊
Come and get them.

04:38.560 --> 04:40.480
但是當心了 因為我是一隻狐貍
But watch out, because I'm a fox...

04:40.640 --> 04:42.680
而且像你那可笑的舞台劇上說的一樣
and like you said in your dumb little stage play...

04:42.960 --> 04:45.200
我們食肉動物過去是吃食草動物的
us predators used to eat prey.

04:45.440 --> 04:47.680
而且那殺手的天性還存在於我們的DANA裏
And that killer instinct is still in our "Dunnah."

04:47.920 --> 04:49.960
呃 我很確定那個念DNA
Uh, I'm pretty much sure it's pronounced "DNA."

04:50.160 --> 04:51.600
我知道念什麼 特拉維斯
Don't tell me what I know, Travis.

04:51.840 --> 04:53.760
你嚇不到我的 吉迪恩
You don't scare me, Gideon.

04:54.640 --> 04:56.600
你現在害怕了嗎
You scared now?

04:56.760 --> 04:57.800
看她那抽搐的兔鼻子
Look at her nose twitch!

04:57.960 --> 04:58.960
她很害怕
She is scared!

04:59.000 --> 05:00.440
哭吧 小兔寶寶
Cry little baby bunny.

05:00.520 --> 05:01.680
哭吧
Cry, Cry...

05:05.320 --> 05:07.480
噢 你就是不知道什麼時候放棄 是吧
Oh, you don't know when to quit, do you?

05:14.840 --> 05:16.440
我希望你記住這個時刻
I want you to remember this moment...

05:16.520 --> 05:17.560
你不過就是一隻
the next time you think...

05:17.800 --> 05:20.200
種胡蘿蔔的蠢兔子 除此之外
you will ever be anything more than just a stupid...

05:20.440 --> 05:23.090
你什麼都幹不了
carrot-farming, dumb bunny.

05:27.600 --> 05:28.680
看起來傷的好嚴重
That looks bad.

05:28.880 --> 05:30.370
你還好嗎 朱迪
Are you okay, Judy?

05:30.520 --> 05:32.640
沒事 我還好 不要緊的
Yeah. Yeah, I'm okay.

05:33.560 --> 05:34.600
-給你 -噢
- Here you go. - Oh!

05:34.720 --> 05:36.440
哇噢 你搶回了我們的票
Wow! You got our tickets!

05:36.680 --> 05:37.960
你真棒 朱迪
You're awesome, Judy!

05:38.200 --> 05:41.520
沒錯 那個吉迪恩·格雷根本就是胡說八道
Yeah, that Gideon Grey doesn't know what he's talking about.

05:41.720 --> 05:43.800
其實 有一件事他說對了
Well, he was right about one thing.

05:46.400 --> 05:49.680
我不知道什麼時候放棄
I don't know when to quit.

05:50.060 --> 05:52.210
動物城警察學校

05:51.160 --> 05:52.200
聽著 學員們
Listen up, cadets.

05:52.360 --> 05:53.930
動物城內有十二個
Zootopia has 12 unique...

05:53.350 --> 05:56.280
十五年後

05:54.080 --> 05:56.400
獨特的生態系統
ecosystems within its city limits.

05:56.640 --> 05:57.680
冰原鎮
Tundratown...

05:57.840 --> 05:58.920
撒哈拉廣場
Sahara Square...

05:59.160 --> 06:00.920
雨林區 等等等等
Rainforest District, to name a few.

06:01.360 --> 06:03.320
你們入職之前
You're gonna have to master all of them...

06:03.480 --> 06:05.760
必須要掌握所有的情況 否則會怎樣呢
before you hit the streets, or guess what?

06:06.040 --> 06:07.840
你們會掛掉
You'll be dead!

06:09.120 --> 06:10.920
灼熱沙塵暴
Scorching sandstorm!

06:13.160 --> 06:14.600
鄉巴佬兔子 你掛了
You're dead, Bunny Bumpkin!

06:14.840 --> 06:17.240
千尺大瀑布
1,000-foot fall!

06:17.400 --> 06:18.600
哇噢
Whoa!

06:18.720 --> 06:20.480
吃胡蘿蔔的 你掛了
You're dead, Carrot Face!

06:20.960 --> 06:22.920
冰凍高牆
Frigid ice wall!

06:23.160 --> 06:24.600
嗚呼
Whoop!

06:24.760 --> 06:26.360
你掛了 農場妹
You're dead, Farm Girl!

06:26.760 --> 06:28.200
重量級罪犯
Enormous criminal.

06:29.480 --> 06:31.080
你掛了 掛了 掛了 掛了
You're dead. Dead, dead, dead!

06:37.640 --> 06:38.840
哇噢
Whoa...

06:39.200 --> 06:40.640
掉進廁所
Filthy toilet!

06:40.800 --> 06:42.320
你掛了 毛屁股
You're dead, Fluff Butt.

06:42.880 --> 06:45.160
放棄回家吧 茸茸兔
Just quit and go home, fuzzy bunny!

06:45.400 --> 06:46.480
從來沒有過兔子當警察
There's never been a bunny cop.

06:46.760 --> 06:47.760
-從來沒有 -從來沒有
- Never. - Never.

06:47.840 --> 06:50.440
你不過就是一隻種胡蘿蔔的蠢兔子
Just a stupid, carrot-farming dumb bunny.

07:17.520 --> 07:20.490
作為動物城的市長 我自豪地宣佈
As mayor of Zootopia, I am proud to announce...

07:20.720 --> 07:23.920
我的哺乳動物招募項目
that my Mammal inclusion Initiative has produced...

07:24.160 --> 07:26.730
已經成功地培養出了第一批警校畢業生
its first police academy graduate.

07:27.000 --> 07:28.650
畢業生代表
Valedictorian of her class...

07:28.840 --> 07:32.240
動物城警局有史以來第一個兔子警官
ZPD's very first rabbit officer...

07:32.480 --> 07:34.480
朱迪·霍普斯
Judy Hopps.

07:34.720 --> 07:36.050
噢 天哪
Oh, gosh.

07:38.680 --> 07:40.200
羊市長助理 她的警徽
Assistant Mayor Bellwether, her badge.

07:40.320 --> 07:41.730
-噢 是的 是的 -謝謝
- Oh, yes. Right! - Thank you.

07:41.960 --> 07:43.280
耶 朱迪
Yay, Judy!

07:43.440 --> 07:44.680
朱迪
Judy.

07:44.760 --> 07:48.360
我很榮幸地正式分配你去
it is my great privilege to officially assign you...

07:48.560 --> 07:50.050
動物城的中心
to the heart of Zootopia:

07:50.240 --> 07:51.760
轄區一區
Precinct One.

07:52.000 --> 07:53.920
市中心
City Center.

07:54.800 --> 07:56.680
恭喜你 霍普斯警官
Congratulations, Officer Hopps.

07:57.200 --> 07:58.690
我不會讓你失望的
I won't let you down.

07:58.800 --> 08:00.520
這是我從小到大的夢想
This has been my dream since I was a kid.

08:01.120 --> 08:03.240
對我們小個頭來說這真是相當自豪的一天
It's a real proud day for us little guys.

08:03.480 --> 08:05.080
羊市長助理 讓一下 好嗎 來
Bellwether, make room, will you? Come on.

08:05.160 --> 08:07.440
好了 霍普斯警官 笑燦爛點吧
Okay, Officer Hopps. Let's see those teeth!

08:07.760 --> 08:09.360
-霍普斯警官 看這裏 -請看這邊
- Officer Hopps, right here! - Look this way please!

08:09.560 --> 08:11.000
不要動 微笑
Hold still. Smile!

08:11.680 --> 08:16.510
祝你好運  朱迪

08:13.440 --> 08:14.720
我們真為你感到驕傲 朱迪
We're real proud of you, Judy.

08:14.920 --> 08:16.360
沒錯 也很害怕
Yeah. Scared, too.

08:16.600 --> 08:17.800
-是啊 -真的 就是那種
- Yes. - Really, it's kind of...

08:17.840 --> 08:18.880
又驕傲又害怕
a proud-scared combo.

08:19.040 --> 08:22.480
我是說 動物城 那麼遠 那麼大一個城市
I mean, Zootopia. So far away. Such a big city.

08:22.560 --> 08:23.600
爸爸媽媽
Guys...

08:23.840 --> 08:25.720
我這輩子都在等這一天
I've been working for this my whole life.

08:25.920 --> 08:26.960
我們知道 我們只是
We know. And we're just...

08:27.120 --> 08:29.240
有一點為你興奮 但也很害怕
a little excited for you, but terrified.

08:29.720 --> 08:32.040
我們唯一應該恐懼的是恐懼本身
The only thing we have to fear is fear itself.

08:32.320 --> 08:34.720
還有熊 我們也要害怕熊
And also bears. We have bears to fear, too.

08:34.960 --> 08:36.240
更別說獅子 還有狼
Say nothing of lions and wolves.

08:36.480 --> 08:37.480
-狼？-黃鼠狼
- Wolves? - Weasels.

08:37.720 --> 08:38.800
你還和黃鼠狼打牌呢
You play cribbage with a weasel.

08:38.880 --> 08:39.960
是啊 他總是出老千
Yeah. And he cheats like there's no tomorrow.

08:40.160 --> 08:41.160
你知道嗎 食肉動物
You know what, pretty much...

08:41.320 --> 08:43.080
大多都那樣 而且動物城裏到處都是
all predators. And Zootopia's full of them.

08:43.240 --> 08:44.240
噢 斯圖
Oh, Stu.

08:44.320 --> 08:45.730
狐貍是最壞的
And foxes are the worst.

08:46.000 --> 08:48.570
實際上 你爸說的話有一定道理
Actually, your father does have a point there.

08:48.680 --> 08:50.010
這是他們的天性
It's in their biology.

08:50.240 --> 08:51.440
記得吉迪恩·格雷嗎
Remember what happened with Gideon Grey?

08:51.680 --> 08:53.090
那時我九歲
When I was nine.

08:53.280 --> 08:56.250
吉迪恩·格雷是個混蛋 而且恰好是個狐貍
Gideon Grey was a jerk who happened to be a fox.

08:56.480 --> 08:58.280
我知道很多兔子也是混蛋
I know plenty of bunnies who are jerks.

08:58.520 --> 09:01.170
當然了 我們也知道 毋庸置疑 但是以防萬一
Sure, we all do. Absolutely. But just in case...

09:01.400 --> 09:02.400
我們給你做了一個
we made you a little care...

09:02.520 --> 09:03.560
-保命包裹給你帶著 -嗯哼
- package to take with you. - Mmm-hmm.

09:03.640 --> 09:04.880
我還放了一些零食在裏面
And I put some snacks in there.

09:05.000 --> 09:06.840
-這是懾狐小喇叭 -沒錯 帶著它
- This is fox deterrent. - Yeah, that's safe...

09:07.000 --> 09:08.080
-很安全 -這是防狐噴霧
- to have that. Okay. - This is fox repellent.

09:08.200 --> 09:09.200
小喇叭和噴霧
The deterrent and the repellent...

09:09.280 --> 09:10.360
-這就萬事俱備了 -來看看這個
- that's all she needs. - Check this out!

09:10.440 --> 09:11.760
噢 天吶
Oh, for goodness sake.

09:11.840 --> 09:13.520
她不需要狐貍電擊器 斯圖
She has no need for a fox Taser, Stu.

09:13.760 --> 09:15.960
噢 得了吧 狐貍電槍最實用了
Oh, come on. When is there not a need for a fox Taser?

09:16.240 --> 09:18.760
好吧 行 我會帶上這個 你們不要再說了
Okay, look! I will take this, to make you stop talking.

09:19.000 --> 09:20.720
太棒了 雙贏的結果
Terrific! Everyone wins!

09:20.920 --> 09:23.440
