I'm sorry, sir.

32:01.120 --> 32:03.200
我盡力攔住她了 但她太麻溜了
I tried to stop her. She is super-slippery.

32:03.480 --> 32:05.000
我得去坐下歇會
I gotta go sit down.

32:05.400 --> 32:08.520
夫人 我已經告訴過你了 我們已經竭盡所能
Ma'am, as I've told you, we're doing everything we can.

32:08.760 --> 32:11.080
我的丈夫已經失蹤十天了
My husband has been missing for 10 days.

32:11.280 --> 32:12.560
他叫埃米特·奧獺頓
His name is Emmitt Otterton.

32:12.800 --> 32:13.800
是 我知道
Yes, I know.

32:13.920 --> 32:15.880
他是個花匠
He's a florist.

32:16.160 --> 32:17.520
我們有兩個漂亮的孩子
We have two beautiful children.

32:17.640 --> 32:19.320
他不會就這樣消失的
He would never just disappear.

32:19.680 --> 32:22.440
夫人 我們的探員都非常忙
Ma'am, our detectives are very busy.

32:22.640 --> 32:23.680
求你了
Please.

32:23.760 --> 32:26.600
一定得有人去找我的埃米特
There's got to be somebody to find my Emmitt.

32:26.840 --> 32:27.880
奧獺頓太太
Mrs. Otterton...

32:27.960 --> 32:28.960
我會找到他的
I will find him.

32:29.440 --> 32:30.480
噢
Oh!

32:30.600 --> 32:32.090
謝謝你
Thank you.

32:32.480 --> 32:33.520
-願上帝保佑你 -噢
- Bless you. - Oh!

32:33.600 --> 32:35.280
願上帝保佑你 小兔子
Bless you, little bunny.

32:36.680 --> 32:37.720
噢
Oh.

32:38.000 --> 32:39.080
拿著這個
Take this.

32:39.160 --> 32:41.520
找到我的埃米特 拜託了
Find my Emmitt. Bring him home...

32:41.720 --> 32:43.640
把他帶回我們身邊
to me and my babies, please.

32:45.040 --> 32:46.160
奧獺頓太太 請在門外稍等
Mrs. Otterton, please wait out here.

32:46.400 --> 32:47.970
好的 噢 太謝謝你們了
Of course. Oh, thank you both so much.

32:48.520 --> 32:49.520
就一會
One second.

32:51.000 --> 32:52.680
你被開除了
You're fired.

32:52.880 --> 32:54.000
什麼 為什麼
What? Why?

32:54.240 --> 32:55.480
違抗命令
Insubordination!

32:55.680 --> 32:57.330
現在 我會把這扇門打開
Now. I'm going to open this door...

32:57.520 --> 32:58.880
然後你要告訴那只水獺
and you're going to tell that otter...

32:59.000 --> 33:00.330
你只是個有妄想癥的
you're a former meter maid...

33:00.560 --> 33:02.520
前交通協管員
with delusions of grandeur...

33:02.720 --> 33:04.440
不能接下這個案子
who will not be taking the case!

33:04.680 --> 33:07.490
我剛聽說霍普斯警官要接這個案子
I just heard Officer Hopps is taking the case.

33:07.720 --> 33:09.000
羊市長助理
Assistant Mayor Bellwether.

33:09.200 --> 33:10.560
哺乳動物納招募項目
The Mammal Inclusion Initiative...

33:10.600 --> 33:12.520
真的有所成效
is really starting to pay off.

33:12.800 --> 33:15.280
獅子市長一定會很激動的
Mayor Lionheart is just gonna be so jazzed!

33:15.520 --> 33:16.520
不 不 我們還是先別告訴市長吧
No, no, let's not tell the Mayor just yet.

33:16.760 --> 33:19.490
然後發送 發送成功 就這麼定啦
And I've sent it and it is done, so I did do that.

33:19.720 --> 33:21.720
好了 嗯 這起案件就交由你們妥善處理
All right. Well, I'd say the case is in good hands.

33:21.760 --> 33:24.000
像我們這種小動物真的需要團結在一起 不是嗎
Us little guys really need to stick together, right?

33:24.400 --> 33:25.480
緊密團結
Like glue.

33:25.720 --> 33:27.000
不錯不錯
Good one.

33:27.200 --> 33:29.120
有任何需要就給我打電話
Just call me if you ever need anything, okay?

33:29.400 --> 33:31.200
你在市政廳永遠有我這個朋友 朱迪
You've always got a friend at City Hall, Judy.

33:31.320 --> 33:32.650
好了 拜拜
All right, bye-bye.

33:32.880 --> 33:34.880
謝謝你 女士
Thank you, ma'am.

33:39.400 --> 33:41.880
我給你四十八小時
I will give you 48 hours.

33:42.160 --> 33:43.200
棒
Yes!

33:43.400 --> 33:44.560
就是說兩天內要找到埃米特·奧獺頓
That's two days to find Emmitt Otterton.

33:44.720 --> 33:45.720
好的
Okay.

33:45.800 --> 33:49.930
但是 你要是失敗了 自動請辭
But, you strike out, you resign.

33:50.080 --> 33:52.080
噢 額
Oh! Uh...

33:54.080 --> 33:55.160
好
Okay.

33:55.280 --> 33:56.280
成交
Deal!

33:56.400 --> 33:57.400
很好
Splendid.

33:57.440 --> 34:00.090
豹警官會把完整檔案給你
Clawhauser will give you the complete case file.

34:00.480 --> 34:01.480
給你
Here you go.

34:00.980 --> 34:01.630
失蹤哺乳動物報告

34:01.640 --> 34:03.080
一隻失蹤的水獺
One missing otter.

34:04.840 --> 34:05.840
就這點兒
That's it?

34:06.000 --> 34:09.000
是呀 這是我見過最薄的檔案了
Yikes! That is the smallest case file I've ever seen.

34:09.240 --> 34:11.400
線索 沒有 目擊者 沒有
Leads, none. Witnesses, none.

34:11.600 --> 34:13.090
你還沒法進入電腦系統
And you're not in the computer system yet...

34:13.280 --> 34:15.440
所以 資源 也沒有
so resources, None!

34:15.680 --> 34:17.090
希望你沒有把自己的職業生涯
Oh, I hope you didn't stake your career...

34:17.280 --> 34:18.930
都賭在這起案子上
on cracking this one!

34:19.200 --> 34:21.240
好吧 最後出現地點
Okay. Last known sighting.

34:26.680 --> 34:28.960
能借我用下嗎 謝謝
Can I just borrow... Thank you.

34:32.000 --> 34:33.040
爪子冰棍
Popsicle?

34:33.280 --> 34:34.800
謀殺兇器
The murder weapon.

34:35.040 --> 34:36.450
「爪子冰棍來一個」
Get your popsicle.

34:36.720 --> 34:40.280
沒錯 因為那...那是什麼意思
Yeah. Because that... What does that mean?

34:40.520 --> 34:41.520
意思是
It means...

34:42.320 --> 34:44.720
我有線索了
I have a lead.

34:50.160 --> 34:52.760
嗨 你好啊 又是我
Hi! Hello? It's me, again!

34:52.960 --> 34:55.960
嘿 是嘟嘟警官
Hey, it's Officer Toot-Toot.

34:56.120 --> 34:57.960
噢 不 實際上是霍普斯警官
No. Actually, it's Officer Hopps...

34:58.160 --> 35:00.200
我來是要就一起案件問你些問題
and I'm here to ask you some questions about a case.

35:00.240 --> 35:01.400
什麼事了 交通協管員
What happened, meter maid?

35:01.520 --> 35:02.840
有人把交通錐標偷了嗎
Did someone steal a traffic cone?

35:02.960 --> 35:04.610
那可不是我
It wasn't me.

35:07.560 --> 35:09.000
嘿 胡蘿蔔頭 你會把寶寶吵醒的
Hey, Carrots, you're going to wake the baby.

35:09.160 --> 35:10.160
我得去開工了
I gotta get to work.

35:10.440 --> 35:11.480
先生 這很重要
This is important, sir.

35:11.720 --> 35:14.840
我想你那十美元的爪子冰棍可以靠邊等
I think your $10 worth of popsicles can wait.

35:15.000 --> 35:18.120
小絨兔 我一天可以賺兩百美元好嗎
I make 200 bucks a day, Fluff!

35:18.320 --> 35:21.480
從我十二歲起 每年365天都如此
365 days a year, since I was 12.

35:21.760 --> 35:23.250
時間就是金錢 一邊待著去
And time is money. Hop along.

35:23.480 --> 35:25.240
請你就看看這張照片吧
Please, just look at the picture.

35:25.480 --> 35:26.810
奧獺頓先生在你這買過爪子冰棍 對吧
You sold Mr. Otterton that popsicle, right?

35:26.920 --> 35:27.960
你認識他嗎
Do you know him?

35:28.160 --> 35:29.160
我認識所有人
I know everybody.

35:29.680 --> 35:31.600
我還知道 某個地方
And I also know that, somewhere...

35:31.840 --> 35:32.960
有個玩具店裏的毛絨玩具不見了
there's a toy store missing its stuffed animal...

35:33.080 --> 35:35.760
所以不如你回到你的盒子裏待著去吧
so why don't you get back to your box?

35:36.000 --> 35:37.800
好吧 是你敬酒不吃吃罰酒
Fine. Then we'll have to do this the hard way.

35:39.520 --> 35:41.010
你剛給我的嬰兒車上夾鎖了是嗎
Did you just boot my stroller?

35:41.280 --> 35:43.000
尼克拉斯·王爾德 你被捕了
Nicholas Wilde, you are under arrest.

35:43.360 --> 35:45.840
哈 為什麼 傷害了你的感情嗎
Ha! For what? Hurting your feelings?

35:46.080 --> 35:47.200
逃稅重罪
Felony Tax Evasion.

35:47.840 --> 35:51.680
嗯 從你12歲起 每天兩百美元
Yeah, $200 a day, 365 days a year...

35:51.840 --> 35:53.040
每年365天
since you were 12.

35:53.280 --> 35:55.200
一共20年 所以乘以20
That's two decades, so times 20...

35:55.360 --> 35:57.960
那就是146萬美元
which is $1,460,000, I think.

35:58.200 --> 36:00.280
雖然我不過是只蠢兔子
I mean, I am just a dumb bunny...

36:00.400 --> 36:01.731
也指兔子的繁殖能力

36:00.400 --> 36:01.730
但我們兔子的乘法還是不錯的
but we are good at multiplying.

36:01.920 --> 36:03.640
不管怎樣 根據你的納稅申報表
Anyway, according to your tax forms...

36:03.880 --> 36:06.480
你繳納了 讓我看看 零美元
you reported, let me see here... zero!

36:06.720 --> 36:09.370
不幸的是 謊報稅款
Unfortunately, lying on a federal form...

36:09.560 --> 36:10.890
可是違法行為
is a punishable offense.

36:11.240 --> 36:12.520
五年牢獄
Five years jail time.

36:12.720 --> 36:14.880
你口說無憑 我不承認
Well, it's my word against yours.

36:15.920 --> 36:17.640
小絨兔 我一天可以賺200美元好嗎
200 bucks a day, Fluff!

36:17.880 --> 36:20.560
從我12歲起 每年365天都如此
365 days a year, since I was 12.

36:20.800 --> 36:22.480
實際上 你已經供認不諱了
Actually, it's your word against yours.

36:22.720 --> 36:24.480
如果你想要拿到這支筆的話 你就得幫我
And if you want this pen, you're going to help me...

36:24.600 --> 36:26.010
找到這個可憐的失蹤水獺
find this poor, missing otter...

36:26.240 --> 36:27.960
否則的話 你就得在監獄食堂裏
or the only place you'll be selling popsicles...

36:28.120 --> 36:30.160
賣你的爪子冰棍
is the prison cafeteria.

36:31.240 --> 36:33.080
這叫智取 親愛的
It's called a hustle, sweetheart.

36:33.440 --> 36:35.360
她智取你了 啊哈哈哈
She hustled you.

36:39.320 --> 36:42.050
幹得漂亮
She hustled you good!

36:42.240 --> 36:45.360
尼克 你現在也是個警察了 你會需要個警徽的
You a cop now, Nick. You gonna need one of these.

36:46.640 --> 36:47.680
祝你和這毛絨兔子
Have fun...

36:47.800 --> 36:48.920
合作愉快
working with the fuzz!

36:51.200 --> 36:52.610
老實交代吧
Start talking.

36:52.800 --> 36:55.240
我不知道他現在在哪
I don't know where he is.

36:55.440 --> 36:56.560
只是見過他去哪了
I only saw where he went.

36:56.760 --> 36:57.760
行 我們走吧
Great. Let's go.

36:59.160 --> 37:01.000
那可不是你這隻小可愛兔子
It's not exactly a place for, uh...

37:01.280 --> 37:02.440
該去的地方
a cute little bunny.

37:02.640 --> 37:04.400
別說我可愛好嗎 上車
Don't call me cute. Get in the car.

37:04.600 --> 37:06.840
行行行 你是老大
Okay. You're the boss.

37:25.440 --> 37:26.850
嗨
Hi.

37:27.120 --> 37:28.120
你好
Hello?

37:29.960 --> 37:31.290
額 你好
Um, hello?

37:31.600 --> 37:33.520
你好 你好嗎
Hello? Hello?

37:35.520 --> 37:36.520
嗯
Hmm?

37:36.640 --> 37:38.040
-你好 我叫 -噢
- Hello. My name is... - Oh...

37:38.240 --> 37:39.480
你知道的 我得先
You know, I'm going to hit...

37:39.600 --> 37:41.480
讓你暫停一下
the pause button right there...

37:41.680 --> 37:43.840
我們不需要兔兔童子軍餅乾了
because we're all good on Bunny Scout cookies.

37:44.080 --> 37:45.880
不是那個
Uh... no.

37:46.120 --> 37:48.320
我是霍普斯警官 來自動物城警察局
I'm Officer Hopps, ZPD.

37:48.560 --> 37:50.720
正在尋找一名失蹤的哺乳
I'm looking for a missing mammal...

37:50.880 --> 37:52.240
埃米特·奧獺頓 就是這位
Emmitt Otterton, right here...

37:52.480 --> 37:55.000
他是不是經常來這裏呀
who may have frequented this establishment.

37:58.600 --> 37:59.640
嗯
Hmm.

37:59.720 --> 38:02.320
啊 老埃米特
Yeah, Old Emmitt.

38:02.560 --> 38:04.840
好幾周都沒見他了
Haven't seen him in a couple of weeks.

38:05.040 --> 38:08.160
但是 嘿 你應該問問他的瑜伽教練
But, hey, you should talk to his yoga instructor.

38:08.360 --> 38:10.010
我很樂意帶你們到後面去
I'd be happy to take you back.

38:10.160 --> 38:11.490
噢 十分感謝
Oh, thank you so much. I'd appreciate that...

38:11.640 --> 38:13.000
真的太謝謝你了 真的
more than you can imagine, it would be such...

38:13.120 --> 38:14.840
-啊 你沒穿衣服 -唔
- Ohh! You are naked! - Huh?

38:15.160 --> 38:18.000
噢 當然 這是自然主義俱樂部
Oh, for sure, we're a naturalist club.

38:18.200 --> 38:21.240
沒錯 在動物城 每個人皆有無限可能
Yeah. In Zootopia, anyone can be anything.

38:21.520 --> 38:23.440
這些傢伙 他們可以赤裸生活
These guys, they be naked.

38:23.680 --> 38:26.570
楠吉在極樂池的另一頭
Nangi's just on the other side of the Pleasure Pool.

38:34.120 --> 38:35.200
噢 天吶
Oh, boy.

38:35.280 --> 38:37.160
看到這一幕你可還好
Does this make you uncomfortable?

38:37.360 --> 38:40.720
如果你覺得不舒服 就此放棄也沒什麼丟人的
Because if so, there is no shame in calling it quits.

38:41.000 --> 38:42.880
這有什麼 走吧
Yes, there is.

38:43.120 --> 38:45.040
還真是勇氣可嘉
Boy, that's the spirit.

38:46.320 --> 38:47.840
是 有些哺乳動物說
Yeah, some mammals say...

38:47.960 --> 38:49.370
自然主義生活很奇怪
the naturalist life is weird...

38:49.560 --> 38:51.480
但你知道我怎麼看嗎
but you know what I say is weird?

38:51.720 --> 38:53.600
動物穿衣服才最奇怪呢
Clothes on animals!

38:54.400 --> 38:56.050
看到她啦
- Here we go. - Mmm...

38:56.320 --> 38:58.360
如你所見 楠吉是一頭大象
As you can see, Nangi's an elephant...

38:58.560 --> 39:00.880
所以她記憶力非凡
so she'll totally remember everything.

39:01.080 --> 39:02.160
嗨 楠吉
Hey, Nangi.

39:02.400 --> 39:04.050
這些傢伙想問你點事
These dudes have some questions...

39:04.160 --> 39:05.520
關於埃米特 那只水獺
about Emmitt the otter.

39:05.640 --> 39:06.640
誰
Who?

39:06.720 --> 39:08.440
額 埃米特·奧獺頓
Uh... Emmitt Otterton?

39:08.600 --> 39:10.240
上你的瑜伽課
Been coming to your yoga class for like...

39:10.280 --> 39:11.440
快六年了
6 years?

39:11.680 --> 39:13.200
我不記得有這只河貍
I have no memory of this beaver.

39:13.400 --> 39:15.080
其實 他是一隻水獺
He's an otter, actually.

39:15.280 --> 39:17.080
幾周前的星期三 他還來過 記得嗎
He was here a couple Wednesdays ago, remember?

39:17.120 --> 39:18.120
沒印象
No.

39:18.200 --> 39:19.200
對了 他穿了一件
Yeah, he was wearing...

39:19.280 --> 39:21.720
綠色針織毛衣背心
a green cable-knit sweater vest...

39:22.000 --> 39:24.080
和一條新的闊特維長褲
and a new pair of corduroy slacks.

39:24.240 --> 39:27.240
噢 還戴了一條佩斯利花紋領帶 打了一個可愛的溫莎結
Oh, and a paisley tie, sweet Windsor knot.

39:27.440 --> 39:29.280
還系得很緊 你記得嗎 楠吉
Real tight. Remember that, Nangi?

39:29.600 --> 39:30.720
沒印象
No.

39:31.240 --> 39:32.920
對了 我們倆一起送他出門 然後
Yeah, and we both walked him out, and he got into...

39:33.040 --> 39:35.610
他上了一輛銀邊的大破車
this big old white car with a silver trim.

39:35.840 --> 39:38.600
那車該修修啦 第三個汽缸打不著火了
Needed a tune-up. The third cylinder wasn't firing.

39:38.800 --> 39:40.760
-記得嗎 楠吉 -沒印象
- Remember that, Nangi? - No.

39:41.200 --> 39:43.080
呃 你該不會
Uh... You didn't happen to catch...

39:43.200 --> 39:45.560
還記得車牌號吧
the license plate number, did you?

39:45.760 --> 39:48.600
噢 當然了 車牌號是 2 9
Oh, for sure. It was 2-9...

39:48.840 --> 39:50.560
T H D
T-h-d...

39:50.760 --> 39:52.640
-0 3 -0 3 哇哦
- 0-3. - JUDY: 0-3. Wow.

39:52.880 --> 39:54.440
這個信息很重要 謝謝
This is a lot of great info. Thank you.

39:54.480 --> 39:57.600
給你說了嘛 楠吉記憶力超群
Told you Nangi has a mind like a steel trap.

39:57.800 --> 40:01.640
真希望我也能擁有大象的記憶力
I wish I had a memory like an elephant.

40:01.940 --> 40:04.110
密泉綠洲

40:03.080 --> 40:05.120
嗯 我玩的很愉快
Well, I had a ball.

40:05.360 --> 40:06.600
我幫你找到了線索 不用謝
You are welcome for the clue...

40:06.880 --> 40:08.840
既然查車牌這件事白癡都會
and seeing as how any moron can run a plate...

40:09.000 --> 40:11.810
那我就帶走那支筆 和你拜拜咯
I will take that pen and bid you adieu.

40:12.280 --> 40:14.760
車牌 我查不到車牌啊
The plate. I can't run a plate.

40:14.960 --> 40:16.240
我還沒能進入電腦系統
I'm not in the system yet.

40:16.640 --> 40:18.320
請把筆給我
Give me the pen, please.

40:18.600 --> 40:20.090
