She's the bunny that saved my life yesterday!

50:07.120 --> 50:08.450
要不然我早被那個大甜甜圈壓死了
From that giant donut.

50:08.680 --> 50:09.680
就是這個兔子嗎
This bunny?

50:09.840 --> 50:11.490
是啊 嗨
Yeah! Hi!

50:11.720 --> 50:14.040
嗨 你的裙子真好看
Hi. I love your dress.

50:14.320 --> 50:16.040
-噢 謝謝誇獎 -噢
- Oh. Thank you. - Oh.

50:16.360 --> 50:17.360
放他們下來
Put 'em down.

50:21.000 --> 50:22.440
你幫了我大忙
You've done me a great service.

50:22.680 --> 50:24.760
我會幫你找到那只水獺的
I will help you find the otter.

50:25.040 --> 50:29.920
你投我以桃 我報之以李
I will take your kindness and pay it forward.

50:35.520 --> 50:37.090
微笑
Smile.

50:37.720 --> 50:39.400
嘿 嘿 嘿
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

50:41.480 --> 50:43.160
嘿 嘿 嘿
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

50:57.920 --> 50:59.600
奧獺頓是我的花匠
Otterton is my florist.

51:00.200 --> 51:02.440
就像我的家人一樣
He's like a part of the family.

51:02.640 --> 51:05.610
他有重要的事想跟我說
He had something important he wanted to discuss.

51:05.840 --> 51:08.680
所以我派車去接他
That's why I sent that car to pick him up.

51:09.480 --> 51:11.160
但他一直沒來
But he never arrived.

51:11.600 --> 51:12.960
因為他被襲擊了
Because he was attacked.

51:13.200 --> 51:15.800
不 是他襲擊了別人
No. He attacked.

51:16.320 --> 51:17.360
奧獺頓嗎
Otterton?

51:17.600 --> 51:20.600
對 就是他 他發瘋了
Otterton. He went crazy.

51:20.880 --> 51:24.800
幾乎要把車都毀了 把我的司機嚇得半死
Ripped up the car, scared my driver half to death...

51:25.000 --> 51:27.320
然後就消失在夜色當中
and disappeared into the night.

51:27.600 --> 51:30.720
可是 他是一隻善良的小水獺啊
But he's a sweet little otter.

51:30.880 --> 51:35.960
親愛的孩子 雖說我們已經進化了 但本質上
Hmm. My child, we may be evolved, but deep down...

51:36.200 --> 51:38.480
仍然是動物
we are still animals.

51:40.500 --> 51:42.200
圖洪加         藤蔓鎮

51:40.640 --> 51:41.600
如果你想找到奧獺頓
You want to find Otterton,

51:41.680 --> 51:43.640
可以問問我的司機
talk to the driver of that car.

51:43.880 --> 51:45.320
他叫曼查斯
His name is Manchas...

51:45.520 --> 51:48.170
住在雨林區
lives in the Rainforest District.

51:48.360 --> 51:50.800
只有他能告訴你更多信息了
Only he can tell you more.

51:54.640 --> 51:56.240
請問 是曼查斯先生嗎
Mr. Manchas?

51:56.480 --> 51:58.360
我是朱迪·霍普斯 來自動物城警局
Judy Hopps, ZPD.

51:58.600 --> 52:01.680
我們想瞭解一下埃米特·奧獺頓發生了什麼事
We just wanna know what happened to Emmitt Otterton.

52:06.600 --> 52:07.600
你
You...

52:07.840 --> 52:09.000
應該先關心一下
should be asking...

52:10.000 --> 52:12.520
-我身上發生了什麼 -哇哦
- what happened to me. - Whoa!

52:13.040 --> 52:16.040
那是小水獺干的嗎
Uh, a teensy otter did that?

52:16.320 --> 52:17.400
到底發生了什麼
What happened?

52:17.640 --> 52:19.680
他是隻野獸
He was an animal.

52:21.000 --> 52:22.000
四爪
Down...

52:22.320 --> 52:24.520
伏地
on all fours.

52:27.600 --> 52:28.930
野蠻殘暴
He was a savage!

52:39.800 --> 52:40.920
一切毫無預兆
There was no warning.

52:41.160 --> 52:43.970
只是他嘴裏一直喊著 午夜嚎叫
He just kept yelling about the Night Howlers.

52:44.200 --> 52:47.040
一遍又一遍地喊 午夜嚎叫
Over and over. The Night Howlers.

52:47.240 --> 52:50.440
你也知道午夜嚎叫是什麼 對嗎
So you know about the Night Howlers, too?

52:50.720 --> 52:52.050
好 很好
Good. Good, good.

52:52.280 --> 52:53.880
因為午夜嚎叫
Because the Night Howlers...

52:54.000 --> 52:56.890
正是我們來找你談的內容
are exactly what we are here to talk about.

52:57.120 --> 52:58.450
-對吧 -是的
- Right? - Yup.

52:59.320 --> 53:01.240
你只需要開門
So, uh, so you just open the door...

53:01.440 --> 53:02.960
告訴我們你知道的一切
and tell us what you know...

53:03.240 --> 53:05.400
我們也會告訴你我們知道的信息 好嗎
and we will tell you what we know. Okay?

53:07.120 --> 53:09.080
好
Okay.

53:10.160 --> 53:12.080
你這狐貍還真聰明
Clever fox.

53:15.800 --> 53:17.920
曼查斯先生
Mr. Manchas?

53:22.200 --> 53:23.200
老兄
Buddy?

53:23.280 --> 53:24.280
你
Are you...

53:24.440 --> 53:25.440
還好嗎
okay?

53:28.320 --> 53:29.920
跑 快跑
Run. Run!

53:34.920 --> 53:35.960
他怎麼了
What is wrong with him?

53:36.200 --> 53:37.480
我不知道啊
I don't know!

53:42.520 --> 53:43.520
跳
Jump!

53:46.160 --> 53:47.160
快過來
Come on!

53:52.120 --> 53:54.600
頭低下
- Head down! - Oh. Oh!

53:55.240 --> 53:56.480
霍普斯警官呼叫
Officer Hopps to Dispatch.

53:56.720 --> 53:58.370
你瞭解夏奇羊嗎 我們時代
Are you familiar with Gazelle, greatest singer

53:58.520 --> 54:00.280
最偉大的歌手 長著犄角的天使
of our lifetime, angel with horns?

54:00.320 --> 54:01.970
好 別走開 接著看噢
Okay, hold on. Keep watching.

54:02.080 --> 54:03.400
你看她後面那個是誰 快看是誰
Who's that beside her? Who is it?

54:03.440 --> 54:06.720
哇 你真是舞技撩人啊 本傑明·豹豪澤
Wow, you are one hot dancer, Benjamin Clawhauser.

54:08.400 --> 54:10.720
那是我 你覺得是真的嗎
It's me! Did you think it was real?

54:10.880 --> 54:11.880
看起來跟真的一樣
It looks so real!

54:12.040 --> 54:14.640
其實是假的 只是一個新手機軟體 等我一下
It's not, it's just a new app. Hold on a second.

54:14.880 --> 54:16.160
豹豪澤
Clawhauser!

54:16.440 --> 54:18.640
豹豪澤 聽我說 這裏有警情
Clawhauser, listen to me, we have a 10-91!

54:18.760 --> 54:20.170
一隻美洲豹發瘋了
Jaguar gone savage!

54:20.440 --> 54:21.440
藤蔓鎮和圖將加交界
Vine and Tuh-junja!

54:21.640 --> 54:23.210
-是圖洪加 -哇哦
- It's "Tuh-hunga!" - Whoa!

54:23.400 --> 54:25.200
好的 我們馬上增援 霍普斯
Okay, we're sending backup! Hopps?

54:25.440 --> 54:26.850
霍普斯
Hopps!

54:28.440 --> 54:29.440
那裏
There!

54:29.520 --> 54:30.880
上那個纜車
Head for the sky trams!

54:40.240 --> 54:41.840
快進來 胡蘿蔔頭
Get in! Carrots.

54:42.040 --> 54:43.040
胡蘿蔔頭
Carrots!

54:43.160 --> 54:44.160
你快走
Go!

54:45.440 --> 54:47.320
不
No, no, no!

54:47.520 --> 54:48.760
老兄
Buddy.

54:49.000 --> 54:50.840
我們同為食肉動物
One predator to another...

54:50.960 --> 54:52.080
不 不 不要
No, no, no...

54:54.960 --> 54:56.840
夥計 你有點緊張了
Now, I can tell you're a little tense...

54:57.040 --> 54:59.200
我現在給你一點私人空間
so I'm just gonna give you a little personal space! Ah!

55:05.360 --> 55:07.280
兔子 不管怎樣 都不要鬆手
Rabbit, whatever you do, do not let go!

55:08.640 --> 55:10.290
-我要鬆手了 -不 你要幹什麼
- I'm gonna let go! - No, you, what?

55:10.520 --> 55:12.240
-一 二 -別這樣
- One, two... - No...

55:12.400 --> 55:14.360
沒聽到嗎 我剛說別 兔子
I said, do not... Rabbit!

55:19.480 --> 55:22.080
胡蘿蔔頭 你救了我一命
Carrots. You saved my life.

55:22.320 --> 55:24.890
嗯 我們警察就是專門幹這個的
Well. That's what we do at the ZPD.

55:40.560 --> 55:42.520
嗯
Hmm.

55:42.600 --> 55:45.490
這下可好
Well, this should be good.

55:46.400 --> 55:47.730
我本以為這只是一起哺乳動物失蹤案
I thought this was just a missing mammal case...

55:47.920 --> 55:49.410
但看來只是冰山一角
but it's way bigger.

55:49.600 --> 55:51.680
奧獺頓先生不只是失蹤了
Mr. Otterton did not just disappear.

55:51.880 --> 55:55.880
我認為他和這只美洲豹 他們野蠻化了 長官
I believe he and this jaguar, they went savage, sir.

55:56.120 --> 55:58.720
野蠻化 這不是石器時代了 霍普斯
Savage? This isn't the Stone Age, Hopps.

55:58.840 --> 56:00.720
動物才不會野蠻化呢
Animals don't "Go savage."

56:00.960 --> 56:04.080
本來也這麼想 直到見到這一幕
I thought so, too, until I saw this.

56:06.160 --> 56:08.810
什麼 他應該就在這的
What? He was right here.

56:09.040 --> 56:10.560
野蠻化的豹子是嗎
The "Savage" Jaguar?

56:11.080 --> 56:13.760
長官 我親眼所見 他差點咬死我們
Sir, I know what I saw. He almost killed us!

56:14.640 --> 56:16.720
或許所有具有攻擊性的食肉動物
Or, maybe any aggressive predator...

56:16.840 --> 56:19.080
在兔子眼裏都很野蠻
looks savage to you rabbits.

56:19.240 --> 56:20.240
我們撤
Let's go!

56:20.480 --> 56:21.480
等等 長官
Wait, sir.

56:21.640 --> 56:23.290
我不是唯一的目擊者
I'm not the only one who saw him.

56:23.560 --> 56:25.130
尼克
Nick!

56:25.600 --> 56:27.480
你覺得我會相信狐貍說的話嗎
You think I'm gonna believe a fox?

56:27.720 --> 56:29.370
但是 他是關鍵的目擊證人 而且我
Well, he was a key witness, and I...

56:29.600 --> 56:31.520
要麼兩天內找到水獺
Two days to find the otter...

56:31.760 --> 56:33.560
要麼你走人
or you quit.

56:33.760 --> 56:35.760
我們說好了的
That was the deal.

56:36.000 --> 56:37.600
警徽
Badge.

56:42.600 --> 56:44.920
-但是長官 我們 -警徽
- But, sir, we... - Badge!

56:50.440 --> 56:51.560
呃 不行
Uh, no.

56:52.800 --> 56:54.240
你說什麼 狐貍
What did you say, fox?

56:54.440 --> 56:57.960
不好意思 我說 不行
Sorry. What I said was, "No."

56:58.200 --> 57:00.800
她不會把警徽交給你的
She will not be giving you that badge.

57:01.000 --> 57:02.720
聽著 你就給她一件搞笑的馬甲
Look, you give her a clown vest...

57:02.840 --> 57:04.720
一輛搞笑的巡邏車
and a three-wheeled joke-mobile...

57:04.960 --> 57:06.200
卻要求她兩天內偵破一個
and two days to solve a case...

57:06.280 --> 57:07.880
你們兩周都破不了的案子
you guys haven't cracked in two weeks?

57:08.800 --> 57:09.800
是啊
Yeah.

57:09.960 --> 57:11.480
怪不得她要找狐貍幫忙
It's no wonder she needed to get help from a fox.

57:11.720 --> 57:13.800
因為你們誰也不會幫她 對嗎
None of you guys were gonna help her, were you?

57:14.000 --> 57:15.320
-我 -這麼說吧 局長
- Ho... - Here's the thing, Chief.

57:15.360 --> 57:16.800
您給了她四十八小時破案
You gave her the 48 hours...

57:17.000 --> 57:18.960
所以嚴格說來我們還有
so, technically, we still have...

57:19.240 --> 57:21.280
十個小時來找到奧獺頓先生
10 left to find our Mr. Otterton...

57:21.480 --> 57:23.640
而我們現在就要去找了
and that is exactly what we're gonna do.

57:23.840 --> 57:25.080
所以恕我們失陪了
So, if you'll excuse us...

57:25.200 --> 57:28.320
我們還有大線索要查 大案子要破
we have a very big lead to follow and a case to crack.

57:28.480 --> 57:29.810
祝好
Good day.

57:35.880 --> 57:37.160
霍普斯警官
Officer Hopps.

57:59.680 --> 58:01.200
謝謝
Thank you.

58:02.360 --> 58:04.680
永遠別被發現別人影響了你
Never let them see that they get to you.

58:06.040 --> 58:07.200
所以
So...

58:07.440 --> 58:09.760
你也有被影響過嗎
things do get to you?

58:10.040 --> 58:12.360
沒有 我意思是 現在不會了
No, I mean, not anymore...

58:12.560 --> 58:14.160
但我曾經
but I was small...

58:14.280 --> 58:16.520
也像你一樣弱小又敏感來著
and emotionally unbalanced like you once.

58:16.760 --> 58:17.800
呵呵
Har-har.

58:17.880 --> 58:19.800
不 我說真的
No, it's true.

58:20.040 --> 58:23.040
那時我才八九歲
I think I was 8, or maybe 9...

58:23.240 --> 58:25.160
我最大的願望
and all I wanted to do...

58:25.280 --> 58:28.520
就是加入小童子軍
was join the Junior Ranger Scouts.

58:28.720 --> 58:31.120
所以我媽媽努力湊錢
So, my mom scraped together enough money...

58:31.240 --> 58:33.560
給我買了一身新制服
to buy me a brand-new uniform...

58:33.760 --> 58:36.120
因為 我發誓 我肯定會適應得很好
because, by God, I was gonna fit in.

58:36.400 --> 58:39.640
就算我是童子軍裏唯一的食肉動物
Even if I was the only predator in the troop.

58:39.880 --> 58:40.880
唯一的狐貍
The only fox.

58:40.920 --> 58:42.040
好了 尼克
Okay, Nick.

58:42.080 --> 58:43.520
我將成為集體中的一員
I was gonna be part of a pack.

58:43.720 --> 58:45.050
準備好了嗎
Ready for initiation?

58:45.240 --> 58:47.080
嗯 我都迫不及待啦
Yeah. Pretty much born ready.

58:47.720 --> 58:49.000
我當時那麼自豪
I was so proud.

58:51.720 --> 58:52.720
好了
Okay.

58:52.920 --> 58:55.240
現在舉起你的右爪 宣讀誓言
Now, raise your right paw and deliver the oath.

58:55.920 --> 58:58.920
我 尼克拉斯·王爾德 保證成為勇敢
I, Nicholas Wilde, promise to be brave...

58:59.120 --> 59:02.010
忠誠 友愛 誠實的人
loyal, helpful, and trustworthy.

59:03.240 --> 59:06.000
就算你是只狐貍
Even though you're a fox?

59:06.640 --> 59:07.760
什麼
What?

59:10.800 --> 59:12.320
不 不要 我做錯什麼了 你們
No. No! What did I do wrong, you guys?

59:12.360 --> 59:14.440
不 拜託 告訴我我做錯什麼了
No, please! Tell me! What did I do wrong?

59:14.640 --> 59:16.360
我做錯什麼了
What did I do?

59:16.480 --> 59:17.840
不
No...

59:18.200 --> 59:19.560
你不會真以為我們會相信一隻
If you thought we would ever trust a fox...

59:19.640 --> 59:20.720
沒戴嘴套的狐貍吧
without a muzzle...

59:21.280 --> 59:22.770
看著挺機靈的沒想到這麼傻
you're even dumber than you look!

59:24.120 --> 59:25.200
愛哭鬼
Cry baby.

59:25.280 --> 59:27.930
噢 他是要哭了嗎
Aw, is he gonna cry?

59:43.640 --> 59:46.160
那天我得到了兩個教訓
I learned two things that day.

59:46.400 --> 59:47.640
第一
One...

59:47.840 --> 59:51.840
我不會再讓任何人看到我的脆弱
I was never gonna let anyone see that they got to me.

59:52.680 --> 59:54.960
那第二呢
And two?

59:55.160 --> 59:57.760
如果全世界都固執認為
If the world's only gonna see a fox...

59:57.920 --> 1:00:00.280
狐貍是陰險狡猾的
as shifty and untrustworthy...

1:00:00.480 --> 1:00:03.450
那也沒必要去嘗試做好人了
there's no point in trying to be anything else.

1:00:03.640 --> 1:00:07.160
尼克 你不是那樣的人
Nick, you are so much more than that.

1:00:11.360 --> 1:00:12.960
天 看看下面的交通
Boy, look at that traffic down there.

1:00:13.160 --> 1:00:14.760
我們接下來連線交通中心的查克
How about we go out to Chuck in Traffic Central.

1:00:15.000 --> 1:00:16.800
查克 攝像頭看到的情況如何啊
Chuck, how are things looking on the Jam Cams?

1:00:17.880 --> 1:00:19.960
尼克 我很高興你告訴我這些
Nick, I'm glad you told me.

1:00:21.000 --> 1:00:22.410
攝像頭
The Jam Cams.

1:00:22.680 --> 1:00:25.250
-真的 沒事了 -不 不 不 噓
- Seriously. It's okay. - No, no, no.

1:00:25.480 --> 1:00:28.450
交通攝像頭到處都是
There are traffic cameras everywhere!

1:00:28.680 --> 1:00:30.280
滿天都是
All over the canopy!

1:00:30.520 --> 1:00:31.920
不管那只豹子出了什麼事
Whatever happened to that jaguar...

1:00:32.040 --> 1:00:33.200
攝像頭肯定都拍到了
The traffic cams would have caught it!

1:00:33.480 --> 1:00:34.680
-沒錯 -哈哈
- Bingo! - Ho-ho!

1:00:34.840 --> 1:00:36.080
真狡猾啊 機靈鬼
Pretty sneaky, slick!

1:00:36.360 --> 1:00:39.720
但是 如果你之前就沒有權限進入監控系統
However, if you didn't have access to the system before...

1:00:39.960 --> 1:00:43.400
我想牛哄哄局長現在也不會讓你進去的
I doubt Chief Buffalo Butt is gonna let you into it now.

1:00:43.640 --> 1:00:44.840
不會
No.

1:00:45.680 --> 1:00:48.000
但我有個市政廳的朋友或許可以幫忙
But I have a friend at City Hall who might.

1:00:48.960 --> 1:00:51.610
呃 市長 要是您能稍微過目這些重要文件
Sir, if we could just review these very important...

1:00:52.080 --> 1:00:53.080
市長先生
Sir...

1:00:53.200 --> 1:00:54.400
抱歉 先生
I'm so sorry. Sir!

1:00:54.640 --> 1:00:57.680
行了 我知道了 羊市長助理 你來處理吧
Okay. I heard you, Bellwether. Just take care of it.

1:00:58.400 --> 1:01:00.760
拜託了 然後把我下午的行程推掉 我要出去
Please. And clear my afternoon. I'm going out.

1:01:01.000 --> 1:01:02.240
不 不行 但是 您下午要跟
No, no! But, sir, you do have a meeting...

1:01:02.360 --> 1:01:03.440
畜牧動物開會啊
with Herds and Grazing.

1:01:03.520 --> 1:01:04.880
先生 如果我
Sir, if I could just...

1:01:06.680 --> 1:01:08.480
噢 殺了我吧
Oh, mutton chops.

1:01:10.360 --> 1:01:11.770
羊市長助理
Assistant Mayor Bellwether?

1:01:12.000 --> 1:01:13.080
我們需要你的幫助
We need your help.

1:01:13.180 --> 1:01:16.430
市長助理辦公室  請敲門！

1:01:14.720 --> 1:01:16.920
我們想要進入交通攝像頭系統
We just need to get into the traffic cam database.

1:01:25.520 --> 1:01:26.930
軟綿綿的耶
So fluffy!

1:01:27.040 --> 1:01:28.120
喂
Hey!

1:01:28.200 --> 1:01:29.560
綿羊從來不讓我靠這麼近的
Sheep never let me get this close.

1:01:29.760 --> 1:01:31.200
你不能隨便摸綿羊的毛
You can't just touch a sheep's wool!

1:01:31.360 --> 1:01:32.440
像棉花糖一樣誒
It's like cotton candy.

1:01:32.520 --> 1:01:33.520
住手
Stop it!

1:01:33.600 --> 1:01:34.640
看哪裏的
Where to?

1:01:35.200 --> 1:01:38.010
啊 雨林區 藤蔓區和圖洪加交界處
Uh, Rainforest District, Vine and Tujunga.

1:01:38.240 --> 1:01:40.860
動物城交通網絡

1:01:38.360 --> 1:01:40.360
好了 整座城的交通攝像頭都在這
There! Traffic cams for the whole city.

1:01:40.400 --> 1:01:42.520
噢 真挺刺激的
Oh, this is so exciting, actually!

1:01:42.760 --> 1:01:44.400
我從沒參與過這麼重要的事
I never get to do anything this important.

1:01:44.560 --> 1:01:46.880
但你是動物城的市長助理啊
But you're the Assistant Mayor of Zootopia.

1:01:47.080 --> 1:01:49.400
噢 其實就是個名字好聽點的秘書罷了
Oh, I'm more of a glorified secretary.

1:01:49.640 --> 1:01:52.040
我覺得獅子市長只是為了爭取綿羊的選票而已
I think Mayor Lionheart just wanted the sheep vote.

1:01:52.240 --> 1:01:53.560
但他確實給了個挺好的杯子
But he did give me that nice mug.

1:01:53.670 --> 1:01:55.670
世上最棒的爸爸× 市長助理

1:01:54.200 --> 1:01:55.480
-噢 -嗯
- Oh. - Hmm.

1:01:55.720 --> 1:01:57.160
受賞識的感覺蠻好的
Feels good to be appreciated.

1:01:57.440 --> 1:01:58.640
臭綿羊
Smell-wether!

1:01:58.880 --> 1:02:01.530
啊 他喜歡叫這個好玩的昵稱
Ugh. That's a fun little name he likes to use.

1:02:01.760 --> 1:02:03.560
有一次我叫他臭獅子
I called him Lion-fart once.

1:02:03.760 --> 1:02:04.920
他不太樂意 我和你們說
He did not care for that. Let me tell you...

1:02:05.080 --> 1:02:06.240
那天我可倒大霉了
it was not a good day for me.

1:02:06.280 --> 1:02:07.320
我在 市長
Yes, sir?

1:02:07.400 --> 1:02:08.730
我以為你已經幫我推掉下午的行程
I thought you were going to cancel my afternoon!

1:02:09.120 --> 1:02:10.840
噢 天吶 我得走了
Oh, dear. I better go.

1:02:11.120 --> 1:02:12.560
有什麼發現告訴我一聲
Let me know what you find.

1:02:12.720 --> 1:02:14.640
我真高興能
It was really nice for me to be...

1:02:14.880 --> 1:02:15.880
-趁花還沒謝 -噢
- While we're young... - Oh...

1:02:16.000 --> 1:02:17.800
臭綿羊
Smell-wether!

1:02:19.120 --> 1:02:20.880
你猜她睡不著的時候 會不會數自己
You think when she goes to sleep she counts herself?

1:02:21.120 --> 1:02:22.800
閉嘴 好了 交通攝像頭
Oh, shush. Okay, traffic cams.

1:02:23.160 --> 1:02:26.160
圖洪加 圖洪加 找到了
Tujunga, Tujunga... We're in.

1:02:31.880 --> 1:02:34.360
-這些都是誰啊 -額
- Who are these guys? - Ugh.

1:02:34.720 --> 1:02:37.610
森林狼 看看這些傻冒
Timberwolves. Look at these dumb-dumbs.

1:02:42.240 --> 1:02:44.810
我敢打賭肯定有一隻要開始嚎叫了
Bet you a nickel one of them is gonna howl.

1:02:45.040 --> 1:02:46.280
看吧 我說
And there it is.

1:02:46.440 --> 1:02:49.170
狼幹嘛非叫不可呢 這簡直
What is it with wolves and the howling? It's like...

1:02:49.400 --> 1:02:51.240
嚎叫 午夜嚎叫
Howlers. Night Howlers.

1:02:51.480 --> 1:02:53.560
曼查斯怕的就是這個 是狼
That's what Manchas was afraid of! Wolves!

1:02:53.800 --> 1:02:55.120
午夜嚎叫說的就是狼
The wolves are the Night Howlers.

1:02:55.240 --> 1:02:56.360
如果是他們抓走了曼查斯
If they took Manchas...

1:02:56.440 --> 1:02:58.090
他們肯定也抓走了奧獺頓
I'll bet they took Otterton, too.

1:02:58.320 --> 1:03:00.760
我們要做的就是找出他們去了哪
All we gotta do is find out where they went.

1:03:08.280 --> 1:03:09.360
等等 他們哪去了
Wait, where did they go?

1:03:09.440 --> 1:03:11.240
知道嗎 要是我幹了什麼違法亂紀的事
You know, if I wanted to avoid surveillance...

1:03:11.400 --> 1:03:12.600
不想被監控逮到的話
because I was doing something illegal...

1:03:12.840 --> 1:03:13.880
當然我可沒真幹過
which I never have...

1:03:13.960 --> 1:03:15.680
我會走維修中的6B隧道
I would use the maintenance tunnel 6B.

1:03:16.440 --> 1:03:17.600
所以他們就會從
Which would put them out...

1:03:18.160 --> 1:03:19.810
這裏出來
right there.

1:03:20.240 --> 1:03:23.480
好啊 看看你 小神探
Well, look at you, Junior Detective.

1:03:23.680 --> 1:03:25.760
知道嗎 我覺得你
You know, I think you'd actually...

1:03:25.920 --> 1:03:27.840
是塊當警察的料
make a pretty good cop.

1:03:28.080 --> 1:03:29.800
呃 別鬧了
Ugh. How dare you.

1:03:30.080 --> 1:03:31.240
阿卡夏小路
Acacia Alley?

1:03:31.480 --> 1:03:32.600
費卡思地下通道
Ficus Underpass.

1:03:32.840 --> 1:03:34.080
-南部峽谷 -嗯哼
- South Canyon. - Mmm-hmm.

1:03:34.280 --> 1:03:35.400
他們要出城了
They're heading out of town.

1:03:35.960 --> 1:03:37.400
那條路是去哪的
Where does that road go?

1:03:37.670 --> 1:03:42.900
崖邊收容所

1:04:22.160 --> 1:04:23.200
蓋瑞 停下
Gary, quit it!

1:04:23.320 --> 1:04:24.440
你會引起狼嚎的
You're gonna start a howl.

1:04:24.520 --> 1:04:26.160
不是我起的頭
I didn't start it!

1:04:33.200 --> 1:04:34.360
快走
Come on.

1:04:42.240 --> 1:04:44.810
你這只聰明的兔子
You are a clever bunny.

1:05:00.600 --> 1:05:03.720
這裏好像曾經是醫院啊
It looks like this was a hospital.

1:05:16.880 --> 1:05:18.450
嗯 你先請 你是警察
You know, after you. You're the cop.

1:05:27.240 --> 1:05:29.680
-好了 沒問題 -額
- Okay, all clear. - Ugh.

1:05:34.400 --> 1:05:36.680
設備都很新
All this equipment is brand new.

1:05:38.360 --> 1:05:39.360
胡蘿蔔頭
Carrots.

1:05:42.040 --> 1:05:43.080
爪痕
Claw marks.

1:05:43.200 --> 1:05:45.720
是啊 超級大爪痕 我說 什麼動物
Yeah, huge, huge claw marks. I mean, what kind of...

1:06:05.320 --> 1:06:07.160
曼查斯先生
Mr. Manchas.

1:06:17.040 --> 1:06:18.280
是他
It's him.

1:06:18.640 --> 1:06:20.680
找到水獺了
We found our otter.

1:06:20.920 --> 1:06:22.360
奧獺頓先生
Mr. Otterton.

1:06:22.600 --> 1:06:25.840
我是朱迪·霍普斯警官 您太太讓我來找您
My name is Officer Judy Hopps. Your wife sent me to find you.

1:06:26.120 --> 1:06:27.280
我們現在救你出去
We're gonna get you out of here now.

1:06:29.200 --> 1:06:30.480
還是算了
Or not.

1:06:30.680 --> 1:06:32.920
我覺得他不太想回家找他太太
Guess he's in no rush to get home to the missus.

1:06:33.360 --> 1:06:35.240
十一 十二 十三 十四
11,12,13,14...

1:06:35.480 --> 1:06:38.450
不算曼查斯的話 總共有十四個
Not including Manchas, it's 14.

1:06:38.720 --> 1:06:41.480
牛局長說有十四起哺乳動物失蹤案
Chief Bogo handed out 14 missing mammal files.

1:06:41.640 --> 1:06:42.680
他們都在這裏
They're all here.

1:06:43.200 --> 1:06:45.640
所有失蹤的哺乳動物都在這裏
All the missing mammals are right here.

1:06:51.840 --> 1:06:54.520
夠了 別找借口了 醫生
Enough! I don't want excuses, Doctor!

1:06:54.720 --> 1:06:55.800
我要的是答案
I want answers.

1:06:55.880 --> 1:06:57.080
獅子市長 拜託
Mayor Lionheart, please.

1:06:57.360 --> 1:06:58.960
我們已經盡力了
We're doing everything we can.

1:06:59.240 --> 1:07:00.240
真的嗎
Really?

1:07:00.840 --> 1:07:02.120
我這有十幾隻動物
Because I got a dozen and a half animals here...

1:07:02.240 --> 1:07:03.840
瘋得連爹娘都認不出了
who have gone off-the-rails crazy...

1:07:04.080 --> 1:07:05.520
而你找不出原因
and you can't tell me why.

1:07:05.720 --> 1:07:08.450
我可一點都不覺得你們盡力了
Now, I'd call that awfully far from "Doing everything."

1:07:08.680 --> 1:07:09.680
市長
Sir...

1:07:09.920 --> 1:07:11.680
可能需要考慮他們的天性了
it may be time to consider their biology.

1:07:11.920 --> 1:07:13.720
什麼 天性是什麼意思
What? What do you mean "Biology?"

1:07:13.920 --> 1:07:16.570
只有食肉動物野蠻化了
The only animals going savage are predators.

1:07:16.840 --> 1:07:19.520
我們不能隱藏真相 我們得公開這件事
We cannot keep it a secret. We need to come forward.

1:07:20.240 --> 1:07:22.520
嗯 好主意 公開透明
Hmm. Great idea. Tell the public.

1:07:22.760 --> 1:07:24.000
但是你覺得他們
And how do you think they're...

1:07:24.080 --> 1:07:25.680
會怎麼看待市長我呢
gonna feel about their mayor...

1:07:25.920 --> 1:07:27.520
我可是頭獅子
who is a lion?

1:07:27.760 --> 1:07:28.840
那我就完蛋了
I'll be ruined!

1:07:28.920 --> 1:07:30.120
好吧 那牛局長怎麼看
Well, what does Chief Bogo say?

1:07:30.400 --> 1:07:32.440
牛局長還不知情
Chief Bogo doesn't know.

1:07:32.680 --> 1:07:35.490
而我們不能讓他知道
And we are going to keep it that way.

1:07:35.600 --> 1:07:37.520
噢 不 不要 糟了
Oh, no, no, no!

1:07:37.760 --> 1:07:38.800
這裏有人
Someone's here.

1:07:39.040 --> 1:07:40.530
市長 您得離開這裏 快走
Sir, you need to go, now!

1:07:40.760 --> 1:07:42.360
保安 封鎖這片區域
Security! Sweep the area!

1:07:50.440 --> 1:07:52.120
太好了 我們死定了 死定了
Great! We're dead. We're dead.

1:07:52.360 --> 1:07:54.720
就這樣了 我死定了 你死定了 大家都死定了
That's it. I'm dead, you're dead. Everybody's dead!

1:07:54.960 --> 1:07:56.000
你會游泳嗎
Can you swim?

1:07:56.240 --> 1:07:58.920
啥 我會游泳嗎 是的 我會 怎麼了
What? Can I swim? Yes, I can swim. Why?

1:08:10.280 --> 1:08:11.720
不 不
No, no, no!

1:08:18.960 --> 1:08:22.850
胡蘿蔔頭 霍普斯 朱迪
Carrots! Hopps! Judy!

1:08:23.600 --> 1:08:25.200
我們得去告訴牛局長
We gotta tell Bogo!

1:08:25.320 --> 1:08:26.840
哇噢
Wow!

1:08:26.960 --> 1:08:30.800
你真是舞技撩人啊 牛局長
You are one hot dancer, Chief Bogo.

1:08:33.320 --> 1:08:35.000
-牛局長 -沒空
- Chief Bogo! - Not now!

1:08:35.240 --> 1:08:37.240
-等等 那是夏奇羊嗎 -不是
- Wait, is that Gazelle? - No.

1:08:37.400 --> 1:08:40.130
我是夏奇羊 你真是舞技撩人
I'm Gazelle, and you are one hot dancer.

1:08:40.320 --> 1:08:43.130
你也下了這個應用 嗷
You have the app too? Oh...

1:08:43.400 --> 1:08:44.520
局長
Chief!

1:08:44.800 --> 1:08:46.000
豹豪澤 你沒看到我在研究
Clawhauser, can't you see I'm working...

1:08:46.160 --> 1:08:47.360
哺乳動物失蹤案嗎
on the missing mammal cases?

1:08:47.640 --> 1:08:49.640
噢 是啊 當然 對了 長官
Oh, oh, oh! Yes of course! About that, sir.

1:08:50.040 --> 1:08:51.120
剛剛霍普斯警官打電話來說
Officer Hopps just called.

1:08:51.320 --> 1:08:52.320
她找到所有失蹤動物了
She found all of them.

1:08:53.160 --> 1:08:55.160
哇噢 真是厲害
Wow! I'm impressed.

1:08:58.240 --> 1:08:59.520
獅子市長 你有權
Mayor Lionheart, you have the right...

1:08:59.680 --> 1:09:00.880
保持沉默 你所說...
to remain silent. Anything...

1:09:01.120 --> 1:09:03.690
你根本不懂 我是在保護這座城市
You don't understand. I was trying to protect the city!

1:09:03.920 --> 1:09:05.920
你只是想保住烏紗帽而已
You were just trying to protect your job.

1:09:06.200 --> 1:09:09.090
不 聽著 我們還不知道這背後的原因
No. Listen, we still don't know why this is happening.

1:09:09.320 --> 1:09:11.240
這會毀了動物城的
It could destroy Zootopia.

1:09:11.600 --> 1:09:12.760
你有權保持沉默
You have the right to remain silent.

1:09:13.040 --> 1:09:14.160
但你所說的話
Anything you say can and will...

1:09:14.320 --> 1:09:15.840
都會被當做呈堂證供
be used against you in a court of law.

1:09:15.880 --> 1:09:19.040
你有權...
You have the right...

1:09:21.000 --> 1:09:22.200
女士們先生們
Ladies and gentlemammals.

1:09:23.360 --> 1:09:25.010
十四隻哺乳動物失蹤了
14 mammals went missing...

1:09:25.360 --> 1:09:28.960
但全都被我們新上任的警官找到了
and all 14 have been found by our newest recruit...

1:09:29.200 --> 1:09:30.560
她過會兒就會與你們進行交流
who will speak to you in a moment.

1:09:30.800 --> 1:09:31.800
但首先 讓我提醒你們...
But first, let me remind you...

1:09:32.040 --> 1:09:33.040
啊 我好緊張
Ugh. I'm so nervous.

1:09:33.280 --> 1:09:35.000
好了 新聞發佈會小貼士
Okay. Press Conference 101.

1:09:35.200 --> 1:09:36.280
你想表現好的話
You wanna look smart?

1:09:36.480 --> 1:09:37.720
就用你自己的問題回答他們的問題
Answer their question with your own question...

1:09:37.960 --> 1:09:40.930
然後回答你自己的問題 打個比方
and then answer that question. Like this.

1:09:41.160 --> 1:09:42.520
「請問 霍普斯警官
"Excuse me. Officer Hopps...

1:09:42.680 --> 1:09:44.440
能跟我們說說案子的事情嗎」
"Uh, what can you tell us about the case?"

1:09:44.680 --> 1:09:46.200
「嗯 這案子很棘手嗎
"Well, was this a tough case?

1:09:46.400 --> 1:09:48.360
是的 的確很棘手」看懂了嗎
"Yes. Yes, it was." You see?

1:09:48.560 --> 1:09:50.320
你應該跟我一起上台去
You should be there with me.

1:09:50.560 --> 1:09:51.800
我們一起破的案
We did this together.

1:09:52.080 --> 1:09:55.120
我是警察嗎 不 我不是
Well, am I a cop? No. No, I am not.

1:09:55.240 --> 1:09:57.400
可別這麼說
Hmm. Funny you should say that...

1:09:57.560 --> 1:09:59.880
因為 我一直在想
because I've been thinking...

1:10:00.160 --> 1:10:04.560
有個搭檔也挺好的
It would be nice to have a partner.

1:10:09.200 --> 1:10:12.170
給你 可以拿來寫點什麼
Here. In case you need something to write with.

1:10:14.760 --> 1:10:16.000
在220個小時內
At twenty-two hundred hours...

1:10:16.160 --> 1:10:17.650
我們找到所有失蹤動物
we found all these missing animals...

1:10:17.880 --> 1:10:20.240
霍普斯警官 該你上台了
Officer Hopps, it's time.

1:10:20.520 --> 1:10:21.800
他們看起來身體狀況良好
They appear to be in good health, physically...

1:10:21.920 --> 1:10:23.760
但精神不佳
...if not emotionally.

1:10:24.280 --> 1:10:26.360
接下來 話筒交給
So now, I'll turn things over...

1:10:26.520 --> 1:10:29.280
破案的警官
to the officer who cracked the case.

1:10:29.560 --> 1:10:31.210
朱迪·霍普斯警官
Officer Judy Hopps.

1:10:32.880 --> 1:10:34.600
-霍普斯警官 -霍普斯警官
- Officer Hopps! - Officer Hopps!

1:10:34.840 --> 1:10:35.840
這邊
Over here!

1:10:35.960 --> 1:10:36.960
請問吧
Yes?

1:10:37.080 --> 1:10:38.600
能不能告訴我們那些野蠻化的動物是怎麼回事
What can you tell us about the animals that went savage?

1:10:38.880 --> 1:10:43.400
嗯 你所問及的動物
Well, the animals in question, um...

1:10:46.440 --> 1:10:48.560
他們都是不同種族的嗎
Are they all different species?

1:10:48.800 --> 1:10:50.720
是的 是的 的確如此
Yes. Yes, they are.

1:10:52.280 --> 1:10:54.120
好吧 那其中有什麼聯繫嗎
Okay, so what is the connection?

1:10:54.360 --> 1:10:56.320
噢 我們只知道
Oh, all we know is that they...

1:10:56.480 --> 1:10:58.050
他們都是食肉動物
are all members of the predator family.

1:10:58.600 --> 1:11:01.250
所以 只有食肉動物會野蠻化嗎
So, predators are the only ones going savage?

1:11:01.800 --> 1:11:04.000
說得沒... 是 說得沒錯 沒錯
That is ac... Yes, that is accurate. Yes.

1:11:04.280 --> 1:11:05.520
為什麼 為什麼會這樣
Why? Why is this happening?

1:11:05.760 --> 1:11:06.840
我們還不知道
We still don't know.

1:11:09.800 --> 1:11:13.440
這可能與動物天性有關
It may have something to do with biology.

1:11:13.640 --> 1:11:14.840
這是什麼意思
What do you mean by that?

1:11:15.120 --> 1:11:17.040
生物因素
A biological component.

1:11:17.280 --> 1:11:20.560
你懂的 他們的DNA決定的
You know, something in their DNA.

1:11:21.320 --> 1:11:23.640
DNA 能詳細說說嗎
In their DNA? Can you elaborate on that, please?

1:11:23.920 --> 1:11:27.760
好的 我的意思是幾千年前
Yes, what I mean is, thousands of years ago...

1:11:28.840 --> 1:11:33.970
食肉動物依賴於他們的捕食天性
uh, predators survived through their aggressive...

1:11:34.160 --> 1:11:35.840
而生存
hunting instincts.

1:11:35.960 --> 1:11:37.000
由於某種原因
For whatever reason...

1:11:37.520 --> 1:11:39.320
他們似乎回到了
they seem to be reverting back...

1:11:39.920 --> 1:11:41.410
原始的 野蠻的樣子
to their primitive, savage ways.

1:11:41.480 --> 1:11:42.960
就是如此
Of course they did.

1:11:43.840 --> 1:11:45.680
啊 他是要哭了嗎
Aw, is he gonna cry?

1:11:45.920 --> 1:11:47.760
霍普斯警官 這類事件還會再次發生嗎
Officer Hopps, could it happen again?

1:11:48.080 --> 1:11:50.810
有可能 所以我們要保持警惕
It is possible. So we must be vigilant.

1:11:51.000 --> 1:11:54.600
而動物城警局會嚴陣以待 隨時準備保護你們
And we at the ZPD are prepared and are here to protect you.

1:11:54.840 --> 1:11:56.040
會有更多的動物野蠻化嗎
Will more mammals go savage?

1:11:56.280 --> 1:11:57.400
你們採取了哪些保護措施啊
What is being done to protect us?

1:11:57.600 --> 1:11:58.760
你們考慮要把
Have you considered

1:11:58.960 --> 1:12:00.040
食肉動物強制隔離嗎
a mandatory quarantine on predators?

1:12:00.200 --> 1:12:01.770
好了 謝謝你 霍普斯警官
Okay, thank you, Officer Hopps.

1:12:01.960 --> 1:12:03.440
時間到了
Uh, that's all the time that we have.

1:12:03.640 --> 1:12:04.760
問答環節結束
No more questions.

1:12:07.480 --> 1:12:08.600
我表現得好嗎
Was I okay?

1:12:08.680 --> 1:12:10.880
噢 挺好的
Oh, you did fine.

1:12:11.480 --> 1:12:12.760
好快啊
Oh, that went so fast.

1:12:12.840 --> 1:12:14.040
我都沒機會提到你
I didn't get a chance to mention you...

1:12:14.200 --> 1:12:15.440
或者談談我們是怎麼
or say anything about how we...

1:12:15.480 --> 1:12:17.920
噢 我覺得你說的夠多了
Oh, I think you said plenty.

1:12:18.440 --> 1:12:19.600
什麼意思
What do you mean?

1:12:19.840 --> 1:12:22.240
「顯然跟生物因素有關」
Clearly there's a biological component?

1:12:22.520 --> 1:12:25.040
「這些食肉動物可能回到了
"These predators may be reverting back..."

1:12:25.200 --> 1:12:27.280
原始的 野蠻的樣子」
To their primitive, savage ways?"

1:12:27.520 --> 1:12:29.040
你認真的嗎
Are you serious?

1:12:29.360 --> 1:12:31.720
我只是實話實說啊
I just stated the facts of the case.

1:12:31.960 --> 1:12:34.240
我是說 兔子可不會野蠻化
I mean, it's not like a bunny could go savage.

1:12:34.480 --> 1:12:36.280
是啊 但是狐貍會的 是吧
Right. But a fox could, huh?

1:12:36.520 --> 1:12:38.800
尼克 別鬧了 你跟他們不一樣
Nick, stop it. You're not like them.

1:12:39.080 --> 1:12:40.840
現在你還區分出陣營了是吧
Oh, there's a "Them" Now?

1:12:41.080 --> 1:12:42.120
你懂我的意思吧
Ugh. You know what I mean.

1:12:42.240 --> 1:12:43.680
你不是那種食肉動物啊
You're not that kind of predator.

1:12:43.920 --> 1:12:45.330
需要戴嘴套的那種嗎
The kind that needs to be muzzled?

1:12:45.560 --> 1:12:46.840
讓你需要隨身攜帶
The kind that makes you think...

1:12:47.000 --> 1:12:49.480
防狐噴霧的那種嗎
you need to carry around fox repellent?

1:12:49.760 --> 1:12:50.760
對 我第一次見你的時候
Yeah, don't think I didn't...

1:12:50.840 --> 1:12:53.360
就注意到這個小東西了
notice that little item the first time we met.

1:12:53.560 --> 1:12:56.800
好 那我問你 你怕我嗎
So let me ask you a question. Are you afraid of me?

1:12:58.400 --> 1:13:00.760
你覺得我會發瘋嗎
Do you think I might go nuts?

1:13:01.360 --> 1:13:03.080
你覺得我會野蠻化嗎
Do you think I might go savage?

1:13:03.320 --> 1:13:05.400
你覺得我會想要
Do you think I might try to...

1:13:05.480 --> 1:13:06.520
吃掉你嗎
eat you?

1:13:10.280 --> 1:13:11.720
我就知道
I knew it.

1:13:14.000 --> 1:13:16.320
我還以為真的有人會相信我呢 結果 呵
Just when I thought somebody actually believed in me, huh.

1:13:16.560 --> 1:13:20.240
你最好還是別找食肉動物做搭檔了
Probably best if you don't have a predator as a partner.

1:13:26.040 --> 1:13:28.160
不 尼克 尼克
No. Nick. Nick!

1:13:28.400 --> 1:13:30.280
霍普斯警官 你剛剛是被那只食肉動物威脅了嗎
Officer Hopps! Were you just threatened by that predator?

1:13:30.480 --> 1:13:32.130
沒有 他是我朋友
No, he's my friend.

1:13:32.320 --> 1:13:34.120
我們連朋友都不能相信了嗎
We can't even trust our own friends?

1:13:34.320 --> 1:13:36.000
我沒有這麼說 讓一下
That is not what I said! Please!

1:13:36.160 --> 1:13:37.160
我們安全嗎
Are we safe?

1:13:37.240 --> 1:13:39.240
狐貍也野蠻化嗎
Have any of our foxes gone savage?

1:13:39.320 --> 1:13:41.640
壞消息接連席捲這個被恐懼包圍的城市
More bad news in this city gripped by fear.

1:13:39.920 --> 1:13:55.730
冰原鎮悲劇

1:13:41.840 --> 1:13:43.680
這頭馴鹿狀況危險
A caribou is in critical condition...

1:13:43.760 --> 1:13:44.920
它被發瘋的
the victim of a mauling...

1:13:45.000 --> 1:13:46.920
北極熊打傷
by a savage polar bear.

1:13:47.120 --> 1:13:49.600
繼霍普斯警官聲稱此類暴力事件
This, the 27th such attack, comes just one week...

1:13:49.800 --> 1:13:53.000
與食肉動物有關後
after ZPD Officer Judy Hopps connected the violence...

1:13:53.120 --> 1:13:55.850
這一周已經發生二十七起類似案件
to traditionally predatory animals.

1:13:56.160 --> 1:13:57.880
與此同時 由流行巨星夏奇羊
Meanwhile, a peace rally organized...

1:13:56.250 --> 1:14:06.400
和平集會爆發緊張衝突

1:13:58.000 --> 1:13:59.600
組織的和平集會
by pop star Gazelle...

1:13:59.800 --> 1:14:01.160
遭到強烈抵制
was marred by protest.

1:14:01.360 --> 1:14:03.240
滾回森林裏 野獸
Go back to the forest, predator!

1:14:03.480 --> 1:14:04.970
我是大草原來的
I'm from the savanna!

1:14:05.160 --> 1:14:07.000
動物城是一個特別的地方
Zootopia is a unique place.

1:14:06.880 --> 1:14:14.840
夏奇羊表明立場

1:14:07.200 --> 1:14:10.600
是一個瘋狂 美麗又多元的城市
It's a crazy, beautiful, diverse city...

1:14:10.840 --> 1:14:13.160
我們因差異而精彩
where we celebrate our differences.

1:14:13.360 --> 1:14:14.720
這不是我認識的動物城
This is not the Zootopia I know.

1:14:16.320 --> 1:14:19.360
我認識的動物城比這好得多
The Zootopia I know is better than this.

1:14:19.640 --> 1:14:21.760
我們不會盲目地互相指責
We don't just blindly assign blame.

1:14:27.000 --> 1:14:29.120
我們也不知道為什麼這類襲擊持續發生
We don't know why these attacks keep happening...

1:14:30.160 --> 1:14:31.880
但將所有食肉動物
but it is irresponsible...

1:14:31.960 --> 1:14:34.240
打上野獸的標籤是不負責任的行為
to label all predators as savages.

1:14:40.680 --> 1:14:42.720
這不是我的埃米特
That's not my Emmitt.

1:14:45.240 --> 1:14:47.640
我們不能讓恐懼分裂我們
We cannot let fear divide us.

1:14:47.840 --> 1:14:52.360
請把我愛的動物城還回來
Please give me back the Zootopia I love.

1:14:55.560 --> 1:14:56.920
走吧 霍普斯警官
Come on, Hopps.

1:14:57.160 --> 1:14:58.360
新市長要見我們
The new mayor wants to see us.

1:14:58.520 --> 1:15:00.880
市長 為什麼
The mayor? Why?

1:15:01.320 --> 1:15:04.000
你現在可是個大人物了
It would seem you've arrived.

1:15:07.320 --> 1:15:08.730
豹豪澤警官
Clawhauser?

1:15:08.960 --> 1:15:10.560
你在做什麼
What are you doing?

1:15:12.520 --> 1:15:14.320
他們認為 人們走進
They thought it would be better...

1:15:14.560 --> 1:15:16.720
動物城警局時 第一眼看到的
if a predator such as myself...

1:15:16.880 --> 1:15:19.240
不是我這樣的食肉動物
wasn't the first face that you see...

1:15:19.440 --> 1:15:21.560
比較好吧
when you walk into the ZPD.

1:15:21.800 --> 1:15:23.290
什麼
What?

1:15:23.920 --> 1:15:25.440
他們準備把我調去檔案室
They're gonna move me to records.

1:15:25.520 --> 1:15:26.560
就在樓下
It's downstairs.

1:15:27.240 --> 1:15:29.080
就在鍋爐房的旁邊
It's by the boiler.

1:15:31.280 --> 1:15:32.720
霍普斯
Hopps!

1:15:36.430 --> 1:15:38.540
正直 誠實 勇敢

1:15:38.400 --> 1:15:41.080
呃 我不懂
Um, I don't understand.

1:15:41.320 --> 1:15:44.240
我們城市裏百分之九十是食草動物 朱迪
Our city is 90% prey, Judy...

1:15:44.480 --> 1:15:46.920
而他們現在都很害怕
and right now they're just really scared.

1:15:47.720 --> 1:15:50.610
對他們來說你就是英雄 他們信任你
You're a hero to them. They trust you.

1:15:50.800 --> 1:15:53.770
所以我和牛局長希望
And so that's why Chief Bogo and I...

1:15:53.880 --> 1:15:57.080
你可以成為動物城警局的形象代言
want you to be the public face of the ZPD.

1:16:01.880 --> 1:16:04.610
我 不是
I'm... not...

1:16:05.640 --> 1:16:07.290
不是一個英雄
I'm not a hero.

1:16:08.120 --> 1:16:11.480
我來是想讓世界變得更美好 但是
I came here to make the world a better place...

1:16:11.720 --> 1:16:13.210
我似乎搞砸了
but I think I broke it.

1:16:13.440 --> 1:16:17.360
你沒這麼大本事 霍普斯
Don't give yourself so much credit, Hopps.

1:16:17.600 --> 1:16:19.000
這世界本來就不美好
The world has always been broken...

1:16:19.120 --> 1:16:21.120
所以才需要像你這樣的
that's why we need good cops.

1:16:22.720 --> 1:16:23.800
好警察
Like you.

1:16:25.440 --> 1:16:30.320
恕我直言 長官 一個好警察
With all due respect, sir, a good cop...

1:16:30.640 --> 1:16:33.800
應該盡責服務 保護市民
is supposed to serve and protect.

1:16:34.040 --> 1:16:36.120
幫扶城市
Help the city.

1:16:36.520 --> 1:16:38.880
而不是分裂人心
Not tear it apart.

1:16:42.440 --> 1:16:44.600
我不配戴這枚警徽
I don't deserve this badge.

1:16:44.680 --> 1:16:45.800
霍普斯
Hopps...

1:16:46.000 --> 1:16:49.080
朱迪 你今天的成績是你辛苦換來的
Judy, you've worked so hard to get here.

1:16:49.320 --> 1:16:51.680
這是你從小的願望
It's what you wanted since you were a kid.

1:16:51.960 --> 1:16:53.640
你不能放棄啊
You can't quit.

1:16:53.920 --> 1:16:55.800
謝謝你們給我的機會
Thank you for the opportunity.

1:17:14.040 --> 1:17:14.760
騷亂愈演愈烈 城市走向分裂

1:17:15.400 --> 1:17:16.760
一打胡蘿蔔
A dozen carrots.

1:17:17.000 --> 1:17:18.080
-謝謝 -祝您生活愉快
- Thanks. - Have a nice day.

1:17:18.320 --> 1:17:19.320
走吧
Come on.

1:17:25.760 --> 1:17:27.840
嗨 朱迪 朱迪小傢伙
Hey, there, Jude. Jude the dude.

1:17:28.000 --> 1:17:30.840
還記得這個小名兒嗎 怎麼了呀
Remember that one? How we doing?

1:17:31.080 --> 1:17:32.160
很好
I'm fine.

1:17:32.240 --> 1:17:34.600
你不好 你的耳朵耷拉著呢
You are not fine. Your ears are droopy.

1:17:35.040 --> 1:17:38.120
我怎麼這麼自信自己能有所作為
Why did I think I could make a difference?

1:17:38.360 --> 1:17:40.040
因為你一直敢於嘗試 這就是原因
Because you're a trier, that's why.

1:17:40.280 --> 1:17:41.880
你一直如此
You've always been a trier.

1:17:42.080 --> 1:17:43.280
噢 我試過了
Oh, I tried.

1:17:43.520 --> 1:17:45.520
結果讓那麼多無辜的食肉動物
And it made life so much worse...

1:17:45.720 --> 1:17:47.400
生活雪上加霜
for so many innocent predators.

1:17:47.720 --> 1:17:48.720
噢 不是所有噢
Oh, not all of them, though.

1:17:48.840 --> 1:17:49.920
真是說曹操
Speak of the devil.

1:17:50.040 --> 1:17:51.200
曹操到
Right on time.

1:17:51.100 --> 1:17:52.760
吉迪恩·格雷 糕點坊

1:17:53.320 --> 1:17:56.050
那是吉迪恩·格雷嗎
Is that Gideon Grey?

1:17:56.280 --> 1:17:58.200
是的 沒錯 我們現在一起合作了
Yep. It sure is. We work with him now.

1:17:58.480 --> 1:17:59.520
他是我們的搭檔
He's our partner.

1:17:59.600 --> 1:18:00.560
還是多虧了你
And we never would have considered it...

1:18:00.720 --> 1:18:01.760
讓我們敞開心胸
had you not opened our minds.

1:18:01.840 --> 1:18:02.840
沒錯
That's right.

1:18:03.000 --> 1:18:04.120
我是說 這小子現在已經是
I mean, Gid's turned into one of...

1:18:04.320 --> 1:18:05.920
三窩區最頂尖的糕點師之一了
the top pastry chefs in the tri-burrows.

1:18:08.160 --> 1:18:09.730
這
That's...

1:18:09.960 --> 1:18:12.610
你們這麼做真的很酷啊
That's really cool, you guys.

1:18:13.200 --> 1:18:14.440
吉迪恩·格雷
Gideon Grey.

1:18:15.000 --> 1:18:16.080
萬萬想不到啊
I'll be darned.

1:18:16.280 --> 1:18:18.480
嗨 朱迪 我想為我小時候的
Hey, Judy. I'd just like to say I'm sorry...

1:18:18.640 --> 1:18:20.640
行為道歉
for the way I behaved in my youth.

1:18:20.920 --> 1:18:24.120
我那時不夠自信 所以總是一副
I had a lot of self-doubt, and it manifested itself...

1:18:24.280 --> 1:18:26.320
兇神惡煞 恃強凌弱的樣子
in the form of unchecked rage and aggression.

1:18:26.560 --> 1:18:28.640
我當時是個大混球
I was a major jerk.

1:18:29.760 --> 1:18:33.240
嗯 我現在也知道當混球的滋味了
Oh, I know a thing or two about being a jerk.

1:18:34.360 --> 1:18:36.960
不管怎麼說 我給你們帶了一些派
Anyhow, I brought y'all these pies.

1:18:38.440 --> 1:18:39.840
嘿 孩子們 小心別踩到
Hey, kids, don't you run through...

1:18:39.880 --> 1:18:41.320
那些午夜嚎叫[拉丁學名]
that midnicampum holicithias.

1:18:41.480 --> 1:18:42.600
哇 哇 哇
Whoa, whoa, whoa...

1:18:42.760 --> 1:18:44.600
現在這可是四美元一朵的天價花啊 老霍
Well, now, there's a $4 word, Mr. H.

1:18:44.840 --> 1:18:47.440
我們家一直管它們叫午夜嚎叫
My family always just called them Night Howlers.

1:18:48.920 --> 1:18:50.360
等等 你說什麼
I'm so... What did you say?

1:18:50.520 --> 1:18:52.240
噢 他在說花的事兒呢 朱迪
Oh, Gid's talking about those flowers, Judy.

1:18:52.480 --> 1:18:54.050
我種來幫農作物驅蟲
I use them to keep the bugs off the produce...

1:18:54.280 --> 1:18:55.770
但鑒於你叔叔特裏的遭遇
but I don't like the little ones going near 'em...

1:18:56.040 --> 1:18:57.320
我不希望孩子們離那些花過近
on account of what happened to your uncle Terry.

1:18:57.560 --> 1:18:59.440
是啊 特裏在我們小時候吃過一整株
Yeah, Terry ate one whole when we were kids...

1:18:59.560 --> 1:19:00.640
然後整個人都瘋了
and went completely nuts.

1:19:00.920 --> 1:19:03.120
他狠狠咬了你媽媽一口
He bit the dickens out of your mother.

1:19:03.360 --> 1:19:05.600
兔子也可以變野蠻
A bunny can go savage.

1:19:05.880 --> 1:19:07.800
野蠻 這個詞有點嚴重了
Savage? Well, that's a strong word.

1:19:07.920 --> 1:19:09.160
但是真的咬的我疼死了
But it did hurt like the devil.

1:19:09.320 --> 1:19:10.320
對啊 當然疼了
Well, sure it did!

1:19:10.400 --> 1:19:12.000
那一口咬的那麼大
There's a sizable divot in your arm.

1:19:12.080 --> 1:19:13.440
必須是野蠻啊
I'd call that savage.

1:19:13.560 --> 1:19:16.800
午夜嚎叫不是狼 是花
Night Howlers aren't wolves, they're flowers!

1:19:17.040 --> 1:19:19.480
是花讓食肉動物野蠻化的
The flowers are making the predators go savage!

1:19:19.640 --> 1:19:20.680
就是這個
That's it!

1:19:20.840 --> 1:19:22.170
這就是我一直尋找的突破口
That's what I've been missing!

1:19:22.880 --> 1:19:23.880
噢 鑰匙
Oh, keys!

1:19:23.960 --> 1:19:25.280
鑰匙 快點 快點
Keys. Keys, keys! Hurry! Come on!

1:19:25.600 --> 1:19:27.960
噢 謝謝 愛你們 拜
Oh! Thank you! I love you! Bye!

1:19:33.520 --> 1:19:34.520
你知道她在說什麼嗎 邦尼
You catch any of that, Bon?

1:19:34.760 --> 1:19:35.840
完全不懂
Not one bit.

1:19:35.960 --> 1:19:37.480
這樣我就放心了
Oh, that makes me feel a little bit better.

1:19:37.640 --> 1:19:39.640
我以為就我一個人聽不懂呢
I thought she was talking in tongues or something.

1:19:56.960 --> 1:19:58.560
誰啊
Who is it?

1:19:59.000 --> 1:20:00.000
我得找到尼克
I need to find Nick.

1:20:00.120 --> 1:20:01.530
拜託
Please.

1:20:02.760 --> 1:20:03.840
尼克
Nick?

1:20:04.560 --> 1:20:05.840
尼克
Nick!

1:20:08.480 --> 1:20:10.000
噢 尼克
Oh, Nick.

1:20:10.240 --> 1:20:12.040
午夜嚎叫不是狼
Night Howlers aren't wolves.

1:20:12.320 --> 1:20:13.920
是有毒的花
They're toxic flowers.

1:20:14.640 --> 1:20:16.240
我想是有人故意針對食肉動物
I think someone is targeting predators on purpose...

1:20:16.400 --> 1:20:18.720
逼他們野蠻化
and making them go savage!

1:20:19.200 --> 1:20:20.400
哇
Wow.

1:20:21.600 --> 1:20:23.520
真有趣呢
Isn't that interesting?

1:20:26.000 --> 1:20:27.120
等等 拜託
Wait... Wait! Listen...

1:20:27.280 --> 1:20:28.690
我知道你不會原諒我的
I know you'll never forgive me!

1:20:28.880 --> 1:20:29.920
但我不怪你
And I don't blame you.

1:20:30.920 --> 1:20:33.890
我也不會原諒自己 我那麼無知
I wouldn't forgive me either. I was ignorant...

1:20:34.920 --> 1:20:38.560
不負責 心胸狹隘
And irresponsible and small-minded.

1:20:40.040 --> 1:20:42.560
但食肉動物不應該因為我的錯誤而受苦
But predators shouldn't suffer because of my mistakes.

1:20:43.520 --> 1:20:45.440
我得補救這一切
I have to fix this.

1:20:45.960 --> 1:20:48.280
但沒有你我做不到
But I can't do it without you.

1:20:50.560 --> 1:20:53.320
等我們結束這一切
And after we're done...

1:20:53.560 --> 1:20:55.240
你再恨我
you can hate me.

1:20:55.360 --> 1:20:57.880
也不遲啊
And... And that'll be fine.

1:20:58.120 --> 1:21:01.320
因為我是一個過分的朋友
Because I was a horrible friend...

1:21:01.560 --> 1:21:02.920
我傷害了你
and I hurt you...

1:21:03.120 --> 1:21:09.570
你一直都是對的 所以你大可以離開我
and you can walk away knowing that you were right all along.

1:21:09.800 --> 1:21:13.720
我真的是只蠢兔子
I really am just a dumb bunny.

1:21:17.720 --> 1:21:21.280
我真的是只蠢兔子
I really am just a dumb bunny.

1:21:23.000 --> 1:21:26.200
我真的是只蠢兔子
I really am just a dumb bunny.

1:21:26.440 --> 1:21:29.330
別擔心 胡蘿蔔頭 四十八小時之後
Don't worry, Carrots. I'll let you erase it...

1:21:29.440 --> 1:21:30.600
我就刪了它
in 48 hours.

1:21:33.440 --> 1:21:35.880
好啦 來抱抱
All right. Get in here.

1:21:37.800 --> 1:21:41.800
好啦好啦 小兔子 怎麼說哭就哭了
Okay. Oh, you bunnies. You're so emotional.

1:21:42.080 --> 1:21:44.400
好啦 深呼吸
There we go. Deep breath.

1:21:44.600 --> 1:21:46.600
你是不是想偷這只錄音筆呀
Are you just trying to steal the pen?

1:21:46.720 --> 1:21:48.290
是不是呀
Is that what this is?

1:21:49.280 --> 1:21:51.120
你踩到我的尾巴了 抬腳 抬腳
You are standing on my tail, though. Off, off, off, off...

1:21:51.240 --> 1:21:52.240
不好意思
Oh, I'm sorry.

1:21:57.160 --> 1:21:59.810
噢 我以為你們只種胡蘿蔔呢
Ooh, I thought you guys only grew carrots.

1:21:59.960 --> 1:22:01.680
好吃 你有什麼計劃
Mmm. What's the plan?

1:22:01.920 --> 1:22:03.520
我們要追蹤午夜嚎叫
We are gonna follow the Night Howlers.

1:22:03.760 --> 1:22:04.960
好啊 怎麼追
Okay. How?

1:22:05.160 --> 1:22:06.440
知道這貨嗎
Know this guy?

1:22:06.880 --> 1:22:09.000
當然 我告訴你 每個人我都認識
Uh-huh. I told you. I know everybody.

1:22:10.350 --> 1:22:13.650
公爵正版電影

1:22:10.480 --> 1:22:13.450
哈哈 瞧一瞧 看一看 要啥有啥
Well, hello. Step right up. Anything you need, I got it.

1:22:13.650 --> 1:22:16.020
超能豬戰隊 魔馬奇緣 犀牛破壞王

1:22:13.800 --> 1:22:15.130
全是你喜歡的電影
All your favorite movies!

1:22:15.360 --> 1:22:17.800
我還有沒放映的電影喲
I got movies that haven't even been released yet.

1:22:16.380 --> 1:22:18.390
喵阿娜 長頸國歷險記 浮冰奇緣2

1:22:18.480 --> 1:22:21.480
嘿 八五折如何 八折 你說個價 來嘛
Hey, 15% off! 20! Make me an offer! Come on!

1:22:21.720 --> 1:22:25.320
哇 看看這是誰呀 盜版公爵
Well, well, look who it is. The duke of bootleg.

1:22:25.720 --> 1:22:26.720
你來幹嘛 王爾德
What's it to you, Wilde?

1:22:26.760 --> 1:22:28.170
你不該去賣冰棍什麼的嗎
Shouldn't you be melting down a popsicle or something?

1:22:28.400 --> 1:22:29.760
喲 這不是兔兔警官嘛
Hey, if it isn't Flopsy the Copsy.

1:22:30.880 --> 1:22:32.640
我們都知道你偷的
We both know those weren't moldy onions...

1:22:32.800 --> 1:22:34.000
可不是洋蔥
I caught you stealing.

1:22:34.120 --> 1:22:35.320
你要這些午夜嚎叫
What were you gonna do with...

1:22:35.360 --> 1:22:36.440
幹嘛呢 黃肅狼
those Night Howlers, Wezzleton?

1:22:36.560 --> 1:22:38.520
是黃鼠狼 黃鼠狼公爵
It's Weaselton! Duke Weaselton!

1:22:38.800 --> 1:22:40.520
我才不告訴你 兔子
And I ain't talking, rabbit.

1:22:40.800 --> 1:22:42.840
你也沒法逼我開口
And there ain't nothing you can do to make me.

1:22:44.520 --> 1:22:45.520
凍了他
Ice him.

1:22:48.920 --> 1:22:50.000
你這卑鄙老鼠
You dirty rat!

1:22:50.160 --> 1:22:51.160
幹嘛幫她啊 她可是警察啊
Why are you helping her? She's a cop!

1:22:51.440 --> 1:22:54.560
她還是我未來孫女的教母呢
And the godmother to my future granddaughter.

1:22:54.720 --> 1:22:56.640
我要給她起名為朱迪
I'm gonna name her Judy.

1:22:58.720 --> 1:22:59.840
凍了這只黃鼠狼
Ice this weasel.

1:23:00.040 --> 1:23:02.360
好吧 好吧 別這樣 我招 我招
All right, all right, please! I'll talk! I'll talk.

1:23:02.400 --> 1:23:03.890
我偷午夜嚎叫 是要拿去賣
I stole them Night Howlers so I could sell 'em.

1:23:04.080 --> 1:23:05.840
他們的出價我不能不動心啊
They offered me what I couldn't refuse.

1:23:06.000 --> 1:23:07.000
錢
Money.

1:23:07.160 --> 1:23:09.040
你賣給誰了
And to whom did you sell them?

1:23:09.240 --> 1:23:10.480
公羊道格
A ram named Doug.

1:23:10.600 --> 1:23:12.090
我們在地下有個接頭地點
We got a drop spot underground.

1:23:12.320 --> 1:23:13.320
小心點
Just watch it.

1:23:13.440 --> 1:23:15.200
道格可不友好
Doug is the opposite of friendly.

1:23:16.320 --> 1:23:17.840
十分兇狠
He's unfriendly.

1:23:28.000 --> 1:23:29.360
走吧
Come On.

1:23:42.160 --> 1:23:43.920
黃鼠狼沒撒謊
The weasel wasn't lying.

1:23:44.200 --> 1:23:45.610
嗯 看來道格壟斷了
Yeah, looks like old Doug's cornered...

1:23:45.760 --> 1:23:47.120
午夜嚎叫的市場
the market on Night Howlers.

1:24:31.160 --> 1:24:32.650
我是道格
You got Doug here.

1:24:32.800 --> 1:24:34.760
目標是誰
What's the mark?

1:24:35.040 --> 1:24:39.170
撒哈拉廣場的獵豹 明白
Cheetah in Sahara Square. Got it.

1:24:39.400 --> 1:24:40.970
你認真的嗎 我知道他們很快
You serious? Yeah, I know they're fast.

1:24:41.200 --> 1:24:42.280
我能打得中
I can hit him.

1:24:42.480 --> 1:24:44.480
聽著 我能從窗口射中一隻
Listen, I hit a tiny little otter...

1:24:44.680 --> 1:24:46.240
坐在車裏的小水獺
through the open window of a moving car.

1:25:00.480 --> 1:25:02.480
好 完事給你打電話
Yeah, I'll buzz you when it's done.

1:25:02.680 --> 1:25:03.680
或者你可以看新聞
Or you'll see it on the news.

1:25:03.760 --> 1:25:05.170
看哪個先來吧
You know, whichever comes first.

1:25:06.360 --> 1:25:09.640
嘿 道格 開門 你的拿鐵來了
Hey, Doug, open up! We've got your latte.

1:25:09.800 --> 1:25:12.200
好了 沃特和傑西回來了 我要走了
All right. Woolter and Jesse are back, so I'm leaving now.

1:25:12.440 --> 1:25:13.520
掛了
Out.

1:25:13.600 --> 1:25:15.170
嘿 你要去哪 你要去哪兒 回來
Hey. Where are you going? Get back here!

1:25:15.280 --> 1:25:17.200
你在幹嘛 他會看到你的
What are you doing? He's gonna see you!

1:25:17.600 --> 1:25:19.200
你在看什麼 嘿
What are you looking at? Hey!

1:25:19.240 --> 1:25:21.600
不管你在想什麼 都別想了
Whatever you're thinking, stop thinking it. Carrots!

1:25:22.600 --> 1:25:23.680
胡蘿蔔頭
Carrots!

1:25:24.080 --> 1:25:26.000
這次最好多加點奶泡
It better have the extra foam this time.

1:25:29.280 --> 1:25:30.280
嘿 開門
Hey, open up!

1:25:30.440 --> 1:25:32.680
你在幹嘛 你把我們困在這裏了
What are you doing? You just trapped us in here.

1:25:32.920 --> 1:25:34.570
我們得把這些證據送到警局
We need to get this evidence to the ZPD!

1:25:35.080 --> 1:25:36.730
好 這不是嗎 拿到了
Okay. Great! Here it is. Got it!

1:25:36.960 --> 1:25:38.840
-不 是所有的 -等等 什麼
- No. All of it! - Wait, what?

1:25:42.680 --> 1:25:45.160
噢 棒極了 你現在又成列車長了是吧
Oh, great, you're a conductor now, huh?

1:25:45.280 --> 1:25:46.690
嘿 聽著 想讓這老破車開動
Hey, listen. It would take a miracle...

1:25:46.800 --> 1:25:48.160
只能靠奇跡了
to get this rust-bucket going.

1:25:50.120 --> 1:25:51.840
哇噢 老天顯靈了
Well. Hallelujah.

1:25:52.120 --> 1:25:54.480
實驗室出了點狀況
We kinda got a situation at the lab.

1:25:54.640 --> 1:25:56.210
現在更糟了
Oh, it just got worse!

1:25:58.000 --> 1:25:59.200
任務完成
Mission accomplished.

1:25:59.320 --> 1:26:00.360
我現在拉一下勝利的
Would it be premature for me...

1:26:00.520 --> 1:26:01.840
嘟嘟號角 會很幼稚嗎
to do a little victory toot-toot?

1:26:01.920 --> 1:26:04.360
好吧 就一下
All right. One toot-toot.

1:26:06.720 --> 1:26:09.240
好了 這個心願已達成
Well, I can cross that off the bucket list.

1:26:20.120 --> 1:26:22.690
我可能得撤銷剛剛那個勝利嘟嘟了
I may have to rescind that victory toot-toot.

1:26:24.520 --> 1:26:25.880
也許只是冰雹呢
Maybe that's just hail.

1:26:26.320 --> 1:26:27.520
給我過來
Come here!

1:26:29.800 --> 1:26:30.920
退後
Back off! Oh!

1:26:36.040 --> 1:26:37.120
他來啦
Incoming!

1:26:39.760 --> 1:26:40.760
胡蘿蔔頭
Carrots!

1:26:41.000 --> 1:26:42.360
別停 繼續開
Don't stop! Keep going!

1:26:42.560 --> 1:26:43.800
不 不 拜託你別停
No, no! Please stop!

1:26:44.040 --> 1:26:45.760
別讓車停下
Do not stop this car!

1:27:08.160 --> 1:27:09.440
加速 尼克 加速
Speed up, Nick! Speed up!

1:27:09.680 --> 1:27:10.920
對面有車來了
There's another train coming!

1:27:11.160 --> 1:27:12.730
相信我 加速
Trust me. Speed up!

1:27:16.840 --> 1:27:17.960
快停車
Stop the train!

1:27:19.880 --> 1:27:20.960
嘿
Hey!

1:27:21.040 --> 1:27:22.640
需要幫忙嗎
Need some help?

1:27:26.160 --> 1:27:27.520
噢 不 不不不 太快了
Oh, no, no, no! Too fast! Too fast!

1:27:27.600 --> 1:27:28.600
停下
Hold on!

1:27:41.000 --> 1:27:42.760
我想我們該下車了
I think this is our stop!

1:27:51.680 --> 1:27:54.330
好吧 也許 有些證據還在呢
Okay, maybe some of the evidence survived.

1:28:03.840 --> 1:28:05.360
一切都沒了
Everything is gone.

1:28:05.600 --> 1:28:07.840
我們什麼都沒了
We've lost it all.

1:28:09.520 --> 1:28:10.880
除了這個
Oh, except for this.

1:28:11.160 --> 1:28:13.810
-噢 尼克 太棒了 -嗷
- Ow. - Ooh, Nick! Yes!

1:28:13.920 --> 1:28:16.040
來吧 我們得趕緊去警局
Come on! We gotta get to the ZPD.

1:28:16.760 --> 1:28:18.880
從國家歷史博物館穿過去
Cut through the Natural History Museum!

1:28:30.560 --> 1:28:31.600
到啦
There it is!

1:28:31.680 --> 1:28:32.680
朱迪
Judy!

1:28:33.400 --> 1:28:34.840
朱迪
Judy!

1:28:35.120 --> 1:28:36.840
羊市長
Mayor Bellwether!

1:28:37.120 --> 1:28:38.320
我們查明原因了
We found out what's happening.

1:28:38.360 --> 1:28:40.160
有人用毒鏢射擊食肉動物
Someone's darting predators with a serum.

1:28:40.360 --> 1:28:42.200
這就是他們野蠻化的原因
That's what's making them go savage.

1:28:42.440 --> 1:28:45.250
我真為你感到驕傲 朱迪 你做的太棒了
I'm so proud of you, Judy. You did just a super job!

1:28:45.480 --> 1:28:47.680
謝謝您 女士
Thank you, ma'am.

1:28:51.240 --> 1:28:53.080
你怎麼知道在哪裏找到我們
How did you know where to find us?

1:28:53.320 --> 1:28:55.040
現在起我來接手這案子吧
I'll go ahead and I'll take that case now.

1:28:55.240 --> 1:28:56.520
我看
Uh, you know what?

1:28:56.680 --> 1:29:00.320
不如還是尼克和我直接送到警局吧
I think Nick and I will just take this to the ZPD.

1:29:05.000 --> 1:29:06.040
跑
Run.

1:29:07.240 --> 1:29:08.570
抓住他們
Get them.

1:29:12.400 --> 1:29:13.440
啊
Ahh!

1:29:14.040 --> 1:29:15.120
胡蘿蔔頭
Carrots!

1:29:16.120 --> 1:29:17.690
我扶著你
I got you!

1:29:17.800 --> 1:29:19.240
沒事的 我們走
Come here, come here.

1:29:21.400 --> 1:29:23.440
好了 現在 放輕鬆
Okay, now just relax.

1:29:23.800 --> 1:29:25.760
掉了 吃藍莓嗎
Whoops... Blueberry?

1:29:26.040 --> 1:29:27.040
不了
Pass.

1:29:28.840 --> 1:29:30.920
出來吧 朱迪
Come on out, Judy.

1:29:31.160 --> 1:29:32.360
拿著箱子
Take the case.

1:29:32.560 --> 1:29:33.600
給牛局長
Get it to Bogo.

1:29:33.880 --> 1:29:35.530
我不會把你留下的 絕對不會
I'm not gonna leave you behind. That's not happening.

1:29:35.760 --> 1:29:36.960
我走不了
I can't walk.

1:29:37.200 --> 1:29:38.200
我們會想到辦法的
Just... We'll think of something.

1:29:38.360 --> 1:29:40.640
我們是同一隊的 朱迪
We're on the same team, Judy.

1:29:40.880 --> 1:29:44.770
懷才不遇 不受重視
Underestimated, underappreciated.

1:29:45.000 --> 1:29:47.080
你不覺得受夠了嗎
Aren't you sick of it?

1:29:49.880 --> 1:29:53.600
食肉動物 或許他們是個高膽大
Predators. They may be strong and loud...

1:29:53.800 --> 1:29:57.440
但食草動物數量是他們的十倍
but prey outnumber predators 10 to 1.

1:30:01.160 --> 1:30:02.160
想想吧
Think of it.

1:30:02.400 --> 1:30:04.280
百分之九十的人口
90% of the population...

1:30:04.480 --> 1:30:06.640
聯合起來對抗共同的敵人
united against a common enemy.

1:30:07.240 --> 1:30:09.280
我們將無堅不摧
We'll be unstoppable.

1:30:15.280 --> 1:30:16.800
在那裏
Over there!

1:30:20.640 --> 1:30:21.640
救命
Help!

1:30:33.440 --> 1:30:34.640
你看 你應該乖乖待在
Well, you should have just stayed...

1:30:34.800 --> 1:30:36.080
胡蘿蔔農場的 對吧
on the carrot farm, huh?

1:30:36.320 --> 1:30:38.800
真是遺憾啊 我以前挺喜歡你的
It really is too bad. I... I did like you.

1:30:39.000 --> 1:30:41.520
你想怎麼樣 殺了我嗎
What are you going to do? Kill me?

1:30:42.800 --> 1:30:44.640
噢 當然不會啦
No, of course not.

1:30:44.840 --> 1:30:45.840
他會
He is.

1:30:46.240 --> 1:30:49.000
不 噢 尼克
No! Oh, Nick!

1:30:49.760 --> 1:30:52.280
沒錯 警察 國家歷史博物館裏
Yes, police! There's a savage fox...

1:30:52.400 --> 1:30:54.120
有一隻發狂的狐貍
in the Natural History Museum.

1:30:54.320 --> 1:30:56.440
朱迪警官已倒下 請趕快來支援
Officer Hopps is down! Please, hurry.

1:30:56.880 --> 1:30:59.000
不 尼克 別被控制啊
No. Nick, don't do this. Fight it.

1:30:59.880 --> 1:31:02.120
噢 但他不能自控呀 不是嗎
Oh, but he can't help it, can he?

1:31:02.360 --> 1:31:04.560
因為食肉動物生來就
Since preds are just biologically...

1:31:04.720 --> 1:31:06.800
有可能野蠻化
predisposed to be savages.

1:31:18.240 --> 1:31:20.680
天吶 想想明天的頭版新聞
Gosh. Think of the headline!

1:31:20.880 --> 1:31:24.850
英雄警察被發狂狐貍殺害
Hero cop killed by savage fox.

1:31:26.120 --> 1:31:28.040
這就是你要的 食草動物懼怕食肉動物
So that's it? Prey fears predator...

1:31:28.200 --> 1:31:29.690
然後你繼續掌權
and you stay in power?

1:31:29.960 --> 1:31:31.400
嗯 差不多吧
Yeah, pretty much.

1:31:31.640 --> 1:31:32.680
不會管用的
It won't work!

1:31:32.960 --> 1:31:35.360
恐懼總會管用
Fear always works.

1:31:35.560 --> 1:31:36.840
即使要我毒射動物城裏
And I'll dart every predator...

1:31:36.960 --> 1:31:38.720
所有的食肉動物也在所不惜
in Zootopia to keep it that way.

1:31:41.760 --> 1:31:42.920
噢 尼克
Oh, Nick.

1:31:43.440 --> 1:31:44.720
不
No.

1:31:47.200 --> 1:31:48.560
再見啦 小兔子
Bye-bye, bunny.

1:31:53.960 --> 1:31:55.000
血
Bleh...

1:31:55.080 --> 1:31:59.240
鮮血噴涌 血流成河 然後一命嗚呼
Blood! Blood! Blood and death.

1:31:59.480 --> 1:32:00.720
好啦 你演得太用力了
All right, you know, you're milking it.

1:32:00.920 --> 1:32:02.160
還有 我想我們成功了 成功了
Besides, I think we got it. I think we got it.

1:32:02.400 --> 1:32:04.640
我們得到證據啦 謝嘍 囉嗦羊
We got it up there, thank you, Yakety-yak!

1:32:04.800 --> 1:32:06.450
你陳述得太完美了
You laid it all out beautifully.

1:32:06.640 --> 1:32:07.640
什麼
What?

1:32:07.680 --> 1:32:09.320
噢 你是在找血清嗎
Yeah... Oh, are you looking for the serum?

1:32:09.560 --> 1:32:10.560
噢 血清在這兒呢
Well, it's right here.

1:32:10.760 --> 1:32:12.200
你手裏的那把武器裏
What you've got in the weapon there?

1:32:12.360 --> 1:32:14.640
裝的是藍莓 我家農場裏種的
Those are blueberries. From my family's farm.

1:32:15.920 --> 1:32:17.760
很好吃喲 你應該嘗嘗
They are delicious. You should try some.

1:32:17.960 --> 1:32:21.240
我嫁禍過獅子市長 我也能嫁禍你們
I framed Lionheart. I can frame you, too.

1:32:21.440 --> 1:32:23.760
你口說無憑 我不會承認的
It's my word against yours.

1:32:24.160 --> 1:32:25.960
噢 其實
Ooh, actually...

1:32:26.200 --> 1:32:27.690
即使要我毒射動物城裏
And I'll dart every predator...

1:32:27.840 --> 1:32:29.250
所有的食肉動物也在所不惜
in Zootopia to keep it that way.

1:32:30.000 --> 1:32:31.280
你已經供認不諱了
...it's your word against yours.

1:32:31.920 --> 1:32:35.080
這叫做智取 親愛的 崩
It's called a hustle, sweetheart. Boom.

1:32:43.430 --> 1:32:49.900
前任羊市長被捕入獄

1:32:43.600 --> 1:32:44.960
近期困擾動物城的動物襲擊事件
Former mayor Dawn Bellwether is behind bars today...

1:32:45.520 --> 1:32:47.280
幕後黑手前任市長道恩·領頭羊
guilty of masterminding the savage attacks...

1:32:47.400 --> 1:32:49.440
今日被捕入獄
that have plagued Zootopia of late.

1:32:49.640 --> 1:32:51.440
她的前任 裏奧多·獅子心
Her predecessor, Leodore Lionheart...

1:32:50.480 --> 1:33:04.030
獅子市長打破沉默

1:32:51.600 --> 1:32:53.170
否認知情她的陰謀
denies any knowledge of her plot...

1:32:53.400 --> 1:32:55.640
聲稱他只是為了保護城市
claiming he was just trying to protect the city.

1:32:55.920 --> 1:32:58.280
我囚禁那些動物是錯誤的嗎
Did I falsely imprison those animals?

1:32:58.480 --> 1:32:59.680
是的 這不應該
Well, yes. Yes, I did.

1:32:59.960 --> 1:33:01.840
這種做法就是典型的
It was a classic "Doing the wrong thing...

1:33:02.000 --> 1:33:03.650
「出於好心 做了壞事」
"For the right reason" Kind of a deal.

1:33:03.880 --> 1:33:05.530
此外 醫生宣稱
In related news, doctors say...

1:33:04.440 --> 1:33:09.030
午夜嚎叫治療證實有效

1:33:05.720 --> 1:33:07.960
午夜嚎叫解毒劑在治療
the Night Howler antidote is proving effective...

1:33:08.200 --> 1:33:10.960
受害食肉動物上 證實有效
in rehabilitating the afflicted predators.

1:33:14.240 --> 1:33:15.240
埃米特
Emmitt.

1:33:15.600 --> 1:33:17.960
噢 埃米特
Oh, Emmitt.

1:33:21.720 --> 1:33:22.760
謝謝你
Thank you.

1:33:25.720 --> 1:33:27.370
我小的時候
When I was a kid...

1:33:27.600 --> 1:33:31.160
我以為動物城是個完美的地方
...L thought Zootopia was this perfect place.

1:33:31.360 --> 1:33:35.800
以為大家都能和睦相處 每個人皆有無限可能
Where everyone got along and anyone could be anything.

1:33:37.000 --> 1:33:38.240
結果發現
Turns out...

1:33:38.400 --> 1:33:40.120
現實生活總比貼紙上的口號
real life's a little bit more complicated...

1:33:40.200 --> 1:33:42.850
要複雜得多
than a slogan on a bumper sticker.

1:33:43.040 --> 1:33:44.760
現實生活很糟糕
Real life is messy.

1:33:46.680 --> 1:33:50.160
我們都有自己的局限 我們都會犯錯
We all have limitations. We all make mistakes.

1:33:50.560 --> 1:33:52.360
所以 樂觀地說
Which means, hey, glass half-full...

1:33:52.480 --> 1:33:54.760
我們都有很多共同之處
we all have a lot in common.

1:33:55.000 --> 1:33:57.730
我們越努力去瞭解彼此
And the more we try to understand one another...

1:33:57.960 --> 1:34:00.850
就越會發現彼此的與眾不同
the more exceptional each of us will be.

1:34:01.840 --> 1:34:03.680
但我們總得一試
But we have to try.

1:34:05.040 --> 1:34:07.560
所以 不管你是什麼動物
So, no matter what type of animal you are...

1:34:07.720 --> 1:34:09.210
從最大只的大象
from the biggest elephant...

1:34:10.160 --> 1:34:12.730
到我們的第一隻狐貍
to our first fox...

1:34:14.080 --> 1:34:18.050
我請求你們 努力嘗試
I implore you... Try.

1:34:18.240 --> 1:34:21.680
讓這個世界變得更美好
Try to make the world a better place.

1:34:23.320 --> 1:34:24.360
從心審視自己
Look inside yourself...

1:34:24.560 --> 1:34:26.210
並認識到 改變
and recognize that change...

1:34:27.000 --> 1:34:28.960
需要從你做起
starts with you.

1:34:30.360 --> 1:34:31.880
從我做起
It starts with me.

1:34:32.880 --> 1:34:36.200
從我們身邊做起
It starts with all of us.

1:34:44.480 --> 1:34:47.290
好了好了 閉嘴
All right. All right, enough! Shut it!

1:34:47.480 --> 1:34:51.320
我們今早來了些新成員
We have some new recruits with us this morning...

1:34:51.560 --> 1:34:52.720
包括我們的第一隻狐貍
including our first fox.

1:34:53.520 --> 1:34:54.880
誰在乎呢
Who cares?

1:34:55.040 --> 1:34:56.240
哈 長官 你應該給自己準備好
Huh, you should have your own line...

1:34:56.320 --> 1:34:57.400
一份鼓舞人心的發言稿
of inspirational greeting cards, sir.

1:34:57.640 --> 1:34:58.800
閉上你的嘴 王爾德
Shut your mouth, Wilde.

1:34:59.360 --> 1:35:00.850
分配任務
Assignments.

1:35:01.080 --> 1:35:03.560
灰熊佐利 尖牙狼 德爾加多警官
Officers Grizzoli, Fangmeyer, Delgato...

1:35:04.240 --> 1:35:05.570
冰原鎮特警隊
Tundratown SWAT.

1:35:05.840 --> 1:35:07.880
熊咆洛 河馬斯 狼法德
Snarlov, Higgins, Wolfard...

1:35:08.040 --> 1:35:09.920
臥底行動
undercover.

1:35:10.160 --> 1:35:12.600
霍普斯 王爾德
Hopps, Wilde.

1:35:12.800 --> 1:35:14.160
交通協管
Parking duty.

1:35:14.400 --> 1:35:16.000
解散
Dismissed.

1:35:16.240 --> 1:35:17.920
開個玩笑啦
Just kidding!

1:35:18.160 --> 1:35:19.760
我們收到警報 大草原區中心
We have reports of a street racer...

1:35:19.840 --> 1:35:21.250
出現一名飆車黨
tearing up Savannah Central.

1:35:21.920 --> 1:35:23.840
找到他 抓回來
Find him, shut him down.

1:35:24.280 --> 1:35:26.720
是所有兔子車技都這麼爛
So, are all rabbits bad drivers...

1:35:26.800 --> 1:35:27.960
還是只有你
or is it just you?

1:35:29.960 --> 1:35:31.160
噢 抱歉
Oops. Sorry.

1:35:32.360 --> 1:35:33.960
狡猾兔子
Sly bunny.

1:35:34.480 --> 1:35:35.480
蠢笨狐貍
Dumb fox.

1:35:35.640 --> 1:35:37.520
你知道你是愛我的
You know you love me.

1:35:37.760 --> 1:35:39.440
我知道嗎
Do I know that?

1:35:39.520 --> 1:35:41.480
對 沒錯 我知道
Yes. Yes, I do.

1:35:56.120 --> 1:35:58.240
先生 你時速高達115英里
Sir, you were going 115 miles per hour.

1:35:58.360 --> 1:35:59.960
你最好有個好借口
I hope you have a good explanation.

1:36:01.720 --> 1:36:02.760
閃電
Flash?

1:36:02.960 --> 1:36:04.960
閃電閃電 瞬息萬變
Flash? Hundred yard dash?

1:36:08.400 --> 1:36:10.920
尼克
Nick.

1:36:12.880 --> 1:36:15.280
晚上好 動物城
Good evening, Zootopia!

1:36:15.480 --> 1:36:17.760
大家一起來 舉起你們的爪
Come on, everybody, put your paws up!

1:37:25.760 --> 1:37:27.440
讓我看到你們的爪
Put your paws in the air. Come on!

1:39:06.800 --> 1:39:07.800
來吧
Come on!

1:39:10.280 --> 1:39:11.690
和我一起 尾巴擺起來
Shake your tails with me. Come on!

1:39:13.120 --> 1:39:14.120
耶
Yeah!
